DESCRIPTION:<b>FCC’s 6th ANNUAL YARD SALE -- </b><b>Saturday\, May 11 from 
 9:00 a.m. to 2:00 p.m.</b><br> <br><br>We are collecting new and gently use
 d items for our yard sale (please\, no clothes). <br><br><u><b>Cutoff date 
 for donations is Wednesday\, May 8!</b></u> <br><br><br>Just like last year
 \, you can drop off your donations in the Guild Room (near the fireplace ar
 ea) weekdays from 9:30am to 5pm\, but please give the office a quick call b
 efore coming by\, if possible (973-744-4856.)&nbsp\; There is no one in the
  office on Saturdays .<br><br>To make things a little bit easier\, we’d lik
 e to ask that if you are donating books\, to put them in shopping bags.&nbs
 p\; Also\,<b> please clean/dust off your items before bringing them in!</b>
  <br><br><ul><li><b>We are looking for volunteers to help move donations to
  the Tower Room on Friday evening\, May 10th at 7pm.</b>&nbsp\; If we have 
 many hands this should take about an hour.</li><li><b>If you can help the d
 ay of the sale </b>(for a few hours or the entire day)\, please let Deb or 
 Anne know.&nbsp\; We ALWAYS have a great time!</li><li><b>The Youth Group i
 s hosting a Bake Sale.&nbsp\; If you’d like to make something\, </b>please 
 contact Deb (due to food allergies\, please list the ingredients). Proceeds
  to benefit their Mission Trip this Summer. &nbsp\; </li></ul>&nbsp\;<i><b>
 All proceeds will go towards the ministries of FCC!</b></i><br><br><u>Any q
 uestions\, please contact:</u><br>Deb Duhamel 857-891-0951&nbsp\; <a href="
 mailto:debbieduhamel@hotmail.com" target="_blank">debbieduhamel@hotmail.com
 </a><br>Anne Garty 973-746-8309&nbsp\; <a href="mailto:agarty14@comcast.net
 " target="_blank">agarty14@comcast.net</a>
LAST-MODIFIED:20190503T194253Z
LOCATION:First Congregational Church\, 40 S Fullerton Ave\, Montclair\, NJ 
 07042
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:6th Annual Yard Sale
