DESCRIPTION:FCC Christmas Open House!  Saturday\, December 17\, 2pm - 6pm \
 n\nJohn & Ann Ralosky and Nancy & Luis Pi-Sunyer invite you to their homes 
 (please call church for address.)\n\nJoin us for an afternoon in Montclair'
 s oldest continuous home (built in 1723!) for a time of treats both sweet a
 nd savory\, mulled wine\, egg nog and a generous helping of holiday cheer! 
 \n\nOnce a year our two families take down the dividing wall in this histor
 ic house and combine our two homes together\, welcoming all our friends fro
 m FCC. \n\nWe'll provide entrees\, beverages and sweets\, but we'd love for
  you to add to the feast! \nIf you are able\, please bring an appetizer\, s
 ide dish or dessert.  If you can just bring yourself\, that's gift enough\,
  too!\n\nRSVP to Rena Majeed at admin@fccmtc.com\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20161205T181502Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:FCC Christmas Open House
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
