CREATED:20180907T153910Z
DESCRIPTION:<b>All are welcome for a new season of Underground Church begin
 ning September 22nd at 5 pm. </b><br>&nbsp\;<br>During our Saturday evening
  gatherings\, the Underground Church travels back to our earliest Christian
  roots.&nbsp\; We seek to recapture the excitement and community of Jesus' 
 early followers through worship that is simple yet profound\, communal yet 
 personal\, comforting yet inspiring.&nbsp\; We live the questions much as J
 esus' friends did as they sought ways to transform the world through the si
 mple acts of a shared and loving community.<br><br><b>We will gather at the
  home of Deb and Julie Matz-Rees.&nbsp\; <u>Please RSVP to Julie</u></b> at
  <a href="mailto:juliemarie.matz@gmail.com">juliemarie.matz@gmail.com</a> a
 nd join us in the transformative power of opening hearts to the Holy Spirit
  and to each other. <br>&nbsp\;<br><u><b>Need a ride?&nbsp\;</b></u> "The U
 nderground Church&nbsp\; Express" will meet you in the FCC parking lot and 
 drive you to our meeting place\, and drive you back after our gathering!&nb
 sp\; Just be in the parking lot behind the church at 4:15PM and a member of
  the Underground Church family will be there to greet you.&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20180907T153910Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Underground Church\, 5pm (RSVP for location)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
