DESCRIPTION:August 18\, September 15\, October 20 (in church library or Cre
 ation Room\, TBA)<br> <p><strong><span>Join us for a summer of friendship\,
  fun and faith!</span></strong></p><p><span>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ gro
 up of First Congregational Church\, and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ commu
 nity we would love for you to join us!  We gather on the first Friday each 
 month for a social event (pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\, etc) and on 
 the third Friday of each month we gather for Full Spectrum Spirituality\, a
  supportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, an
 d delve into our faith and scripture through a queer lens. To learn more\, 
 please contact Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448
 ).</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230713T172556Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Full Spectrum Spirituality (LGBTQ+ Group) Third Friday (Time & loca
 tion TBA)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
