UID:37pfm80s2lmc4oi87blupfrqgf@google.com
CREATED:20181106T205345Z
DESCRIPTION:All are welcome!<br>During our Saturday evening gatherings\, th
 e Underground Church travels back to our earliest Christian roots.&nbsp\; W
 e seek to recapture the excitement and community of Jesus' early followers 
 through worship that is simple yet profound\, communal yet personal\, comfo
 rting yet inspiring.&nbsp\; We live the questions much as Jesus' friends di
 d as they sought ways to transform the world through the simple acts of a s
 hared and loving community.<br><br><b>We will gather at the home of Deb and
  Julie Matz-Rees.&nbsp\; Please RSVP to Julie</b> at <a href="mailto:juliem
 arie.matz@gmail.com">juliemarie.matz@gmail.com</a> and join us in the trans
 formative power of opening hearts to the Holy Spirit and to each other. <br
 >&nbsp\;<br>Need a ride?&nbsp\; "The Underground Church&nbsp\; Express" wil
 l meet you in the FCC parking lot and drive you to our meeting place\, and 
 drive you back after our gathering!&nbsp\; Just be in the parking lot behin
 d the church at 4:15PM and a member of the Underground Church family will b
 e there to greet you.
LAST-MODIFIED:20181106T205345Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Join us for Underground Church\, 5pm
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
