DESCRIPTION:<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none"> One of our mo
 st beloved Holy Week traditions at FCC is our Maundy Thursday supper.  Our 
 menu echoes the Mediterranean meal that Jesus would have shared with his fr
 iends.  FCC will provide the grilled lamb. We are asking for contributions 
 of specific side dishes(rice pilaf\, salads\, cookies\, etc.)  To sign up g
 o to: <a href="https://tinyurl.com/maundysignup"><b>https://tinyurl.com/mau
 ndysignup</b></a></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination:none"><span
  style="language:en-US\;mso-ligatures:none" lang="en-US"></span></p><p><spa
 n lang="en-US"></span></p><p><span lang="en-US"></span><span lang="en-US">T
 o help offset the cost of the meal we are asking for $10 donation for indiv
 iduals\, $5 for children under 8 and $20 for families.&nbsp\; Payment can b
 e<span>&nbsp\; </span>mailed or brought to church on Sundays (</span><span 
 lang="en-US">please make a note on your check saying “Maundy Thursday.”</sp
 an><span lang="en-US">) </span><span lang="en-US">To ensure enough food and
  to hold your place\, reservations and prepayment are required (call the ch
 urch at 973-744-4856.).</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20180308T213918Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Maundy Thursday Supper in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
