DESCRIPTION:    <br><p>W<span>e are so excited to announce the formation of
  a special Ministry for the FCC LGBTQ+ community!  This group will plan a n
 umber of social events like potluck suppers\, game nights and movie nights\
 , to scripture study\, small support groups and much more.  This first gath
 ering will be a chance to get to know each other\, have some fun\, brainsto
 rm and plan future events. <b> Bring a snack to share!</b><br>While we love
  our allies\, <i><b>at this time we are offering this ministry only for our
  LGBTQ+ community.</b></i><br>Questions\, please contact Alexis Lourenco at
  </span><a href="mailto:alexismlourenco@gmail.com"><span>alexismlourenco@gm
 ail.com</span></a><span> </span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230301T224057Z
