DESCRIPTION:Each month\, FSS will offer explorations into the scriptures an
 d what they mean for us.  This month\, we will focus on the “clobber passag
 es\,” which are so often used to keep LGBTQ+ folks away from the Bible and 
 Christianity in general. We will reflect on what these verses mean for us t
 oday\, and listen for Divine Wisdom. <br><i> <br><b>*</b>Please note: This 
 is a Safe Space Event for LGBTQ+ identified folks only. There will be other
  opportunities for allies to join us!</i>
