DESCRIPTION:MMO Casino Night Spring Fundraiser will take place on Saturday 
 April 30th. The event is shaping up to be one of our best\, with over $15\,
 000 in prizes! If you would like to have a great evening of games\, music\,
  food and fun - all while supporting this important FCC ministry - please g
 o to http://www.mmocasinonight.org/ to buy tickets.\n\nThis will be a night
  of fun and games to raise funds for capital improvements to the school’s f
 acilities. And we want you to come and play!  Parents\, friends and neighbo
 rs are invited for a night of great company\, food\, drink\, music\, prizes
  and of course favorite casino games: Roulette\, Black Jack\, Craps\, Poker
  and more.\n\nAll funds raised will enhance the enjoyment and education of 
 our own MMO Programs' play-based approach to childcare. The more equipment 
 and materials we can get our hands on\, the better the learning experiences
  and development of the children. Things like classroom furniture\, play eq
 uipment\, ID badges\, and science and music installations are just a few it
 ems on the list.\n\nTickets start at only $50 per person.  You can also buy
  High Roller tickets or buy-in to a Poker Tournament. Purchase tickets at h
 ttp://www.mmocasinonight.org/\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20160411T154849Z
