DESCRIPTION:<span><b><i>PLEASE NOTE TIME CHANGE FOR THIS SESSION! </i></b><
 br></span><br><span> </span><br><span>Underground Church is a unique and dy
 namic gathering that combines the intimacy of Jesus' early community with c
 reative and inventive worship experiences.  In the warmth and safety of com
 munity we explore the scriptures\, live out the questions through discussio
 n\,  and share innovative rituals that bring us closer to each other and to
  our still-speaking God.  Together we create the unity of spirit that helps
  us find God's presence in the messy and beautiful experience of living tod
 ay.</span>
