DESCRIPTION:FCC and Reverend Ann are being honored by Vanguard Theater Comp
 any at its Black &amp\; White Gala celebrating D.R.E.A.M. - Diversity\, Rec
 iprocity\, Education\, Awareness &amp\; Mentorship.&nbsp\; <br>&nbsp\;<br>A
 long with TeeRico by Lin Manuel Miranda\, Montclair Film\, Nassan’s Place a
 nd GrassRoots Foundation\, FCC has been chosen for exemplifying Vanguard’s 
 mission.&nbsp\; We are excited to celebrate with Vanguard on November 3rd <
 b>at The Loft in Montclair.</b>&nbsp\; We hope you will join us for an exci
 ting evening of dancing\, dining\, performances and a live auction.<br><br>
 <br><b>Please use the code <u>VIPFCC</u> to unlock a special discounted tic
 ket tier\, called VIP GALA\, for the FCC family!</b>&nbsp\; <a href="https:
 //www.eventbrite.com/e/2018-vanguard-theater-company-dream-gala-tickets-487
 35642619" target="_blank">Click here for more info and to purchase tickets.
 </a><br><br>&nbsp\;<br>We look forward to celebrating with you!
