UID:7j003t64uo6e9571s5t8fguisd@google.com
CREATED:20180205T163024Z
DESCRIPTION:<span lang="en-US"></span><p align="center"><b><i><span>Moments
 of Grace</span></i></b><span><span></span></span></p><p align="center"><i><
 span>&nbsp\;Whatcan we do to ease the pain of a hurting world?&nbsp\; What 
 if we could becomeaware of how we can be an instrument of grace in every mo
 ment?&nbsp\; What if wecould find a way to turn mundane tasks into prayers\
 , lay down our burdens andopen ourselves to be of service to others?&nbsp\;
  Journeywith us&nbsp\;<span>this Saturday</span>&nbsp\;evening as wedelve i
 nto the gospel of Mark.&nbsp\; Jesus reminds us that we don't have to "gain
 the whole world."&nbsp\; And that we should not forfeit our souls.&nbsp\;Be
 cause authentic souls joined together to intentionally live into moments of
 grace can create a powerful energy of healing and wholeness.&nbsp\; </span>
 </i><span><span></span></span></p><p align="center"><i><span>Undergroundchu
 rch travels back to our earliest Christian roots.&nbsp\; We seek to recaptu
 rethe excitement and community of Jesus's early followers through worship t
 hat issimple yet profound\, communal yet personal\, comforting yet inspirin
 g.&nbsp\; Welive the questions much as Jesus's friends did as they sought w
 ays to transformthe world through the simple acts of a shared and loving co
