CREATED:20230209T172352Z
DESCRIPTION:<i><span><span><span>The Journey of Lent Begins with </span></s
 pan></span></i><span><span><span>Ash Wednesday\, February 22 at 7:30pm in t
 he Sanctuary.</span></span></span><h4><span><span><i>"From dust you came an
 d to dust you shall return..."</i></span></span></h4>The season of Lent is 
 a time for going deeper into our faith journey and coming to terms with our
  struggles and our yearning for God. It is a time of reflection that prepar
 es us for the passion of Holy Week and the glory of Easter Sunday.<br> <br>
 We begin with a special Ash Wednesday service. Through song and prayers and
  times of silence we will share the ritual of the imposition of ashes\, a s
 ymbol of our mortality and brokenness\, as well as experience the hope and 
 unity of Holy Communion.<br> <br>This is a deeply meaningful way to begin t
 he season.  If you are new to our tradition and have never been to and Ash 
 Wednesday service\, we encourage you to share it with us. <span>We will bel
 ive-streaming the service over Facebook. </span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230210T221907Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Ash Wednesday Service 7:30pm in the Sanctuary
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
