DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Join us forfriendship\, fun and faith!</b></p><p>Full Spe
 ctrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First CongregationalChurch\, and if you are pa
 rt of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you tojoin us!<span>  </span>W
 e gather on the first Fridayeach month for a social event (pot lucks\, movi
 e nights\, picnics\, etc) <b>and on the third Friday of each month wegather
  on Zoom for Full Spectrum Spirituality</b>\, a supportive group to talkabo
 ut our spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, and delve into our faith andscr
 ipture through a queer lens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Boggess(86
 2-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</p>
