 ood Bank are also welcome (checks should be made out to "Community Food Ban
 k of NJ.")</span></p><p><u><b><span>Most&nbsp\; needed items:</span></b></u
 ></p><p><span><b>Turkeys (MUST BE FROZEN)\,</b> Canned Yams &amp\; Sweet Po
 tatoes\, Gravy (packs and cans)\, Cranberry Sauce\, Canned Vegetables\, Stu
 ffing Mixes\, Instant Mashed Potatoes\, Applesauce\, Canned Fruits\, Bevera
 ges and Boxed Desserts (be sure to check the expiration date).<br>&nbsp\;</
 span></p><p><span>If you cannot stop by on Nov. 20th\, please feel free to 
