UID:735ost2oagugtuq8usgt40m8dp@google.com
CREATED:20230208T211227Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><span>FCC will be hosting MESH (Montclair Emergency Services
  for Hope) meals on the second Saturday of the month<b><span>.</span></b><b
 ><br><br><b><span>Our next meal is scheduled for March 11 between the hours
  of 4:40pm and 6:30pm</span></b></b><u> <b><span>inside the old Office Rest
 aurant building at 619 Bloomfield Avenue in Montclair.</span></b></u><br><b
 r>MESH guests love how friendly\, gracious\, and warm our FCC volunteers ar
 e when we host…and of course\, the guests love the delicious meals\, snacks
 \, and beverages we provide!<br> <br>There are many ways to help…prepare fo
 od\, pick up water\, snacks\, desserts\, help set up\, greet\, and serve me
 als\, and most importantly\, have fun with the guests.</span><span><br><br>
