DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><p><span>Slow Motion Adult Bible Study is hel
 d every Thursday at 7:30pm for approximately an hour on Zoom.<br></span></p
 ><p><span>Our method is to take our time and dig deeply into Scripture\, br
 inging in cultural\, historical\,theological\, and linguistic&nbsp\;backgro
 unds and resources. We utilize Queries(questions posed for consideration an
 d opening\, not to garner answers) and cross-referencing. (There are&nbsp\;
 occasional&nbsp\;dives down theological or linguistic rabbit holes.) Partic
 ipants&nbsp\;are encouraged&nbsp\;to have their favorite translation of the
 &nbsp\;Bible with them.</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><b>Please contact 
 Rev. Jack Cuffari at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com">jack@cuffari.com</a>
  to receive the Zoom link.</b><br></p><u></u></html-blob>
