DESCRIPTION:<span><span><b>Full Spectrum Summer Schedule: </b></span></span
 ><span><u><b><br></b></u></span><br><span><u><b>First Friday Fun:</b></u> <
 /span><br><span>August 4\, September 1\, October 6 (events and locations TB
 A)  </span><b><span></span></b><br><b><span> </span></b><br><b><span>Join u
 s for a summer of friendship\, fun and faith!</span></b><p><span>Full Spect
 rum is the LGBTQ+ group of First Congregational Church\, and if you are par
 t of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you to join us!  We gather on t
 he first Friday each month for a social event (pot lucks\, movie nights\, p
 icnics\, etc) and on the third Friday of each month we gather for Full Spec
 trum Spirituality\, a supportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys
 \, ask questions\, and delve into our faith and scripture through a queer l
 ens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis L
 ourenco (856-332-7448).</span></p>
