 nual Hanging of the Greens Worship Service</b><br></span></p><p><span>Today
  we will begin our season of Advent -- a time of waiting and preparation to
  ready our lives for the birth of Christ.&nbsp\; It is an FCC tradition to&
 nbsp\;prepare our Sanctuary&nbsp\;with a&nbsp\; service of "Hanging of the 
 Greens" -- a&nbsp\;special celebration of the symbols of the season.&nbsp\;
  <br></span></p><p><span>During our worship we will transform our sanctuary
  with colors and greens and lights as we share their special meaning and ex
 perience this season of Advent in a whole new way! </span></p><p>&nbsp\;</p
 >
