  Church) will be led by Cynthia and Julie Rogers (mother and sister of our 
 Youth Director\, John Rogers).  The theme of “Into the Woods and Out of the
   Woods: Journeys through Darkness to Light” will take us on a weekend jour
 ney into the beautiful Pocono Mountain foothills. \nSee brochure on narthex
  table for additional details.\n \nCome for the weekend ($250) or just Satu
 rday ($60).  Please register by December 20.  Come out and join the fun. Co
 ntact Phyllis Stone for more details 917-715-1059\, phyllis.stone@nyu.edu.
