CREATED:20160914T161527Z
DESCRIPTION:“Underground Church” begins September 24!\n\nCan't make it to c
 hurch Sunday morning? Check out "Underground Church" on Saturday\, Septembe
 r 24th at 5 pm in the FCC gym. Entrance to the gym is through the lower doo
 r off The Crescent (across from the parking deck).  John Rogers will be lea
 ding our service.\n\nThe liturgy will bring us back to the simplicity of ea
 rly church. In a circle\, we will share wisdom\, sing\, and celebrate commu
 nion. In place of a sermon\, there will be a short reflection on the sacred
  text with time to reason collectively as a group. \n\nPlease join us as we
  go back to the roots of the Christian tradition and experience the Spirit 
 together.
