DESCRIPTION:<i><b>“Calm in the Storm: Finding our Center in an Anxious Age”
 </b></i><br><br>This year’s Women’s Retreat will be led by Rev. Ann Ralosky
 \, who invites us to take a deep breath and discover the still center of ou
 r lives at a weekend journey in the Connecticut countryside at the Trinity 
 Retreat Center.<br><br>We will discover that inner calm through guided me d
 itation\, mindful breathing and labyrinth walking\, and take time to listen
  deeply to our souls.&nbsp\; We will welcome silent reflection\, journaling
  and great conversation\, emerging renewed and refreshed\, ready to face wh
 atever storms the new year brings.<br><br>The all-inclusive cost is $225 pe
 r person\, double occupancy. All meals included. A deposit of $100 by Dec. 
 14 will hold your reservation. Balance is due Jan. 18. Scholarships may be 
 available. Single rooms depending on availability. Please register by Dec 1
 4th. You may register with a credit card at<u> www.unioncong.org</u>. Click
  the Payments icon on the homepage.&nbsp\; Questions? Contact Karen Ermler 
 at 973-429-7665 or karen.ermler@gmail.com
LAST-MODIFIED:20181012T213659Z
