DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Join us forfriendship\, fun and faith!</b><span> <br></sp
 an></p><p>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First CongregationalChurch\,
  and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you tojoin u
 s!<span>  </span>We gather on the first Fridayeach month for a social event
  (pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\, etc) <b>and onthe third Friday of ea
 ch month we gather on Zoom for Full SpectrumSpirituality\,</b> a supportive
  group to talk about our spiritual journeys\, askquestions\, and delve into
  our faith and scripture through a queer lens. Tolearn more\, please contac
 t Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco(856-332-7448).</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20231228T173106Z
