  birth of Jesus at Christmas.  The Advent Wreath is a spiritual resource th
 at will help to guide you through this season of waiting.  The Children’s E
 ducation Ministry along with the Spirituality & Worship Ministry invite you
  to join in making an Advent Wreath of your own that you will then take hom
 e and enjoy through the season of Advent!  \n\nSo that we will have plenty 
 of supplies for all who would like to participate\, we are asking that folk
 s pre-register.  A $10 donation is requested to help cover the costs of sup
 plies.  If you are able to also donate an extra $5 to help cover the cost f
 or someone who is unable to pay\, your donation is appreciated.  \n
