DESCRIPTION:This Messy Church (June) will be a POTLUCK. No reservations nec
 essary but please something to share. You may choose to bring an appetizer 
 or an entree or a side dish or a salad or a dessert - whatever you'd like. 
 Drinks will be provided. We'll begin to gather at 5:45\, and dinner will st
 art about 6:30 to give everyone a chance to arrive and settle in while we s
 et up our delicious potluck spread.\n\nRather than splitting into small gro
 ups for our normal Messy activities\, we will have the opportunity to spend
  this time all together\, sharing food and friendship with our FCC communit
 y.\n\nThere will be no Messy Church events in July or August but we will re
 convene in the fall. If you have ideas about future Messy Church events or 
 you'd like to join our planning team\, please see Cindy! New voices are wel
 comed.  If you have questions\, please contact Cindy at vickery.cindy@gmail
 .com.\n
