 erground Church" is inspired by the spirit of the early church. We served o
 ne another communion after sharing wisdom in a circle. We also sing the wor
 ds to one of earliest Christian hymns as a community. And\, we feel the joy
  that comes from this simple style of worship. It is a beautiful experience
  to travel back to the roots 
