 tful people from the wisdom of the Bible."</i> -Rabbi Harold Kushner <br> <
 br><span>Many folks at FCC are inspired by the fresh interpretation of scri
 pture they hear during worship but wonder why it sounds so different.  If t
 his is you\, please join us for a thought-provoking exploration in to the s
 criptures through the book\, <b><u><span><a href="https://firstcongmontclai
 r.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=3c5141d050
 &e=d2d6ac503b"><span>Reading the Bible Again for the First Time</span></a> 
 </span></u></b><b><span>by Biblical scholar\, Marcus Borg.  </span></b>Borg
  offers an accessible and deeply insightful understanding of how to read th
 e Bible through the lenses of history and metaphor that lets the scripture 
 come alive. To order the book\, <a href="https://firstcongmontclair.us6.lis
 t-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=511bf04c1b&e=d2d6ac
 503b"><span>CLICK HERE.</span></a><span>  </span></span><br><span><span> </
 span></span><br><b><span>We will cover each chapter over a series of 10 wee
 ks\, <u>approximately every other Thursday</u> on Zoom at 7:00pm from </spa
 n></b><b><span><b><span>September 28 through February 1. </span></b></span>
 </b><br><b><span><b><span><u>F</u></span></b></span></b><span><b><u>ull Cla
 ss Schedule</u>: </b>Sept 28\, Oct 12\, Oct26\, Nov16\, Nov30\, Dec7\, Jan4
 \, Jan18\, Feb1\, Feb15</span><p></p><p></p><p><span>Whether this is the fi
 rst time you've cracked open a bible\, or you've been reading for years\, y
 ou are welcome to join us!  Questions? Email Rev. Ann <a href="mailto:(acra
 losky@msn.com)"><span>(</span></a><a href="mailto:acralosky@msn.com"><span>
 acralosky@msn.com</span></a><a href="mailto:(acralosky@msn.com)"><span>)</s
 pan></a>or Rev. Jack (<a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com"><span>jack@cuffari.
 com</span></a>)</span></p><p><span><u><b>Click </b></u></span><a href="http
 s://us02web.zoom.us/j/87486762412?pwd=N0Z2eVlCNzJPbVM3VmdzZW1GYzZHUT09#succ
 ess"><u><b><span>HERE</span></b></u></a><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/j/
 87486762412?pwd=N0Z2eVlCNzJPbVM3VmdzZW1GYzZHUT09#success"><u><b> </b></u></
 a><span><u><b>to join!  </b></u><b>Meeting ID: 874 8676 2412<br>Passcode: 9
 85645   </b>Phone only? Dial 646 558 8656  </span></p></span>
