 <p><span>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First Congregational Church\,
  and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you to join 
 us!  We gather on the first Friday each month for a social event (pot lucks
 \, movie nights\, picnics\, etc) and on the third Friday of each month we g
 ather for Full Spectrum Spirituality\, a supportive group to talk about our
  spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, and delve into our faith and scriptur
 e through a queer lens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Boggess (862-22
 8-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</span></p>
