DESCRIPTION:<span><strong>Join us for a hike and outdoor worship at spectac
 ular </strong></span><strong><a href="https://www.morrisparks.net/index.php
 /parks/pyramid-mountain-natural-historic-area"><span>Pyramid Mountain</span
 ></a></strong><span><strong> in Boonton</strong>. This beautiful sacred spo
 t was a hunting\, fishing\, and gathering site for the Lenape for more than
  10\,000 years. It’s now part of the Morris County Park Commission and offe
 rs numerous trails and glacial formations. We'll meet at the FCC parking lo
 t at 8:30 am  (40 South Fullerton Ave\, Montclair) to carpool to arrive at 
 the Visitor Center at 9:30. We’ll be doing a moderate hike to </span><a hre
 f="https://bestofnj.com/features/travel/the-best-nj-hiking-trails-pyramid-m
 ountain-tripod-rock-trail/"><span>Tripod Rock</span></a><span> where we’ll 
 have a “Wild Church” outdoor worship experience and then have lunch. Bring 
 your reusable water bottle and lunch and/or snacks.  RSVP to </span><a href
 ="mailto:tracey@traceystephens.com"><span>tracey@traceystephens.com</span><
 /a><span> </span>
