  to join us!  We gather on the first Friday each month for a social event (
 pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\, etc. - but for Sept it's moved to 9/8)
  <b>and on the third Friday of each month we gather for Full Spectrum Spiri
 tuality\, a supportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys\, ask que
 stions\, and delve into our faith and scripture through a queer lens.</b> T
 o learn more\, please contact Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenc
 o (856-332-7448).</span></p></span>
