DESCRIPTION:The American Dream belongs to all of us.  Let's celebrate it!\n
 \nCelebrating the American Dream: an Evening of Solidarity\, Empowerment an
 d Hope\nJanuary 20\, 2017\, 7-8pm in the FCC Sanctuary\nFirst Congregationa
 l Church 40 South Fullerton Avenue\, Montclair\, NJ\n\nAs we prepare to eng
 age a new administration\, BlueWaveNJ and First Congregational Church invit
 e you to join us in raising our voices for progressive values. We’ll hear f
 rom inspiring local leaders and activists who are energized to meet the cha
 llenges ahead.\nThis is a moment for commitment and action. Come\, get ener
 gized with us! \nGather with voices from:\nFirst Congregational Church\nTem
 ple Ner Tamid\nBlueWaveNJ\nNAACP\nACLU\n\nNo RSVP needed -- just come out a
 nd join us!\n
