 llowship\, worship<span width="150" height="112" align="right"></span> and 
 fun!&nbsp\; Entrees and drinks are provided but contributions of side dishe
 s and desserts are welcome. We will join together for prayer\, food and son
 g.&nbsp\; February's Messy Church will be hosted by our Faith in Action Min
 istry. In keeping with Black History Month and our congregation's work in t
 he Kindred Spirits program\,the theme will be<i> "Bridging the Gap: Working
  Racial Justice with Love."</i>&nbsp\; We will be sharing Soul Food (contri
 butions welcome.) <br>Donations welcome but not necessary. All are welcome!
 </span>
