CREATED:20200408T165339Z
DESCRIPTION:<p>Please join us for Underground Church on Saturday\, April 18
 th at 5 pm via Zoom! Together\, we will talk\, sing\, and create sacred spa
 ce that transcends the walls of our homes.&nbsp\; Like Jesus' early followe
 rs\, we will gather together to ease our fears and loneliness by creating a
  community of love and trust.</p><p></p><p><u><b>To take part in Undergroun
 d Church</b></u></p><p>Please get to your computer\, phone\, or tablet (wit
 h camera installed) <b>at 4:55 pm on Saturday</b> and click the link: <a hr
 ef="https://zoom.us/j/438540847" id="ow336" __is_owner="true"><span>https:/
 /zoom.us/j/438540847</span></a>.&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Say yes to any downloads—som
 etimes the software is pre-loaded\, sometimes you have to download the soft
 ware to begin. If you have technical difficulties with videoconferencing <b
 >or would prefer telephone</b>\, dial +1 929 436 2866. Our meeting ID is 43
 8 540 847.<br>&nbsp\;<br>Together\, we will create a sacred space to share\
 , and to hold on to\, that will remind us that no matter how much physical 
 distance we maintain\, we are never alone.&nbsp\; Our space will be virtual
 \, but no less sacred.&nbsp\; All are welcome!</p>
