UID:0davqvmge8ln66ipq45ljt3d7q@google.com
CREATED:20170915T202043Z
DESCRIPTION:We're meeting at 268 PARK STREET IN UPPER MONTCLAIR! (Please RS
 VP)\n\nUnderground Church travels back to our earliest Christian roots.  We
  seek to recapture the excitement and community of Jesus' early followers t
 hrough worship that is simple yet profound\, communal yet personal\, comfor
 ting yet inspiring.  We live the questions much as Jesus's friends did as t
 hey sought ways to transform the world through the simple acts of a shared 
 and loving community.\n\nWe invite you to gather with us on Saturday\, Sept
 ember 30th from 5PM to 6:30PM at the home of Deb and Julie Matz-Rees\, 268 
 Park Street\, Upper Montclair\, to go deeper into the beauty of community. 
  Worship will be informal\, but we will engage through the reading of a sac
 red text\, create space to share what is on our hearts\, and share a simple
  and blessed communion meal of soup and bread\, ending our evening with son
 g and "Spiritual Take-Out."  \nPlease RSVP to Julie at juliemarie.matz@gmai
 l.com\, and let us know if you would like to bring food to share.  But plea
 se remember that that is not an expectation.  This gathering is about the t
 ransformative power of opening our homes and our hearts to the Holy Spirit 
 and to each other.  Everyone is welcome!  - - Elaine Wells\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170921T174314Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Underground Church\, 5pm - - PLEASE NOTE LOCATION!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
