CREATED:20170306T233624Z
DESCRIPTION:Next “Underground Church”  - Saturday\, March 25 at 5 pm! \n \n
 Can't make it to church Sunday morning? Check out "Underground Church!" The
  gathering will be held downstairs in the gym\, which is through the lower 
 door off The Crescent (across from the parking deck). \n \nLed by John Roge
 rs\, our Associate Minister\, "Underground Church" is inspired by the spiri
 t of the early church. We serve one another communion after sharing wisdom 
 in a circle. We also sing the words to one of earliest Christian hymns as a
  community. And\, we feel the joy that comes from this simple style of wors
 hip. It is a beautiful experience to travel back to the roots of the early 
 Christ movement!
LAST-MODIFIED:20170306T233624Z
