CREATED:20170915T202742Z
DESCRIPTION:Special Social Media Messy Church \n\nInterested in raising you
 r social media literacy? \nMark your Calendar for the October 11 Messy Chur
 ch sponsored by FCC’s Social Media Team. This is an exciting intergeneratio
 nal event where we will strengthen relationships and equip ourselves with n
 ecessary tools for  navigating the  internet. \n\nWhat Is Messy Church?\n\n
 Messy Church is an informal and unstructured (“messy”) evening that brings 
 our community together for a simple dinner\, an opportunity to work togethe
 r to create a stronger community within and outside our church walls\, or s
 imply just be. \nWe will provide dinner\, a brief and informal worship expe
 rience\, and either an activity or an opportunity to serve our community. T
 his is a great way to  offer friendship and share in God’s love in a fun\, 
 informal way.\n\n So take a break from the mid-week stress\, and recharge y
 ourself with us!  Please contact Kathleen Korgen at korgenk@gmail.com if yo
 u have any questions.\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170915T202742Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Messy Church\, 6-8pm in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
