 ber 16\, 23\, 30* and October 7*.\n*=Labyrinth will be open.\n\nWhere?  FCC
 ’s front entry walkway!\nAKA:  the “town’s front porch”\n\nWhat?  Foster co
 mmunity relationships.\nListen\, connect\, and pray with neighbors.\nShare 
