DESCRIPTION:<p><span><span>FCC is an inspiring faith community with a rich 
 history -- and we'd love for you to be a part of our future!  If you have b
 een worshipping with us and are interested in becoming a member of our cong
 regation\, or just knowing more about us\,<strong> please join us for 3 Zoo
 m classes </strong>where we will explore the how we believe\, what we stand
  for and what it means to become a member. The classes are engaging and fun
  and a great way to meet other folks at FCC!</span><br><strong>If you have 
 been with us in person or online only\, you are welcome! All new members wi
 ll be welcomed in a <u>special ritual during worship on March 19</u>.</stro
 ng><br>If you're interested please email Rev. Ann at </span><a href="mailto
 :acralosky@msn.com"><u><span>acralosky@msn.com</span></u></a></p>
