DESCRIPTION:Back by popular demand – FCC’s 2nd Annual Yard Sale! Spring is 
 FINALLY here\, and what\nbetter time to start cleaning out your basement\, 
 cupboards\, closets\, garage\, etc. As you\nbegin\, ask yourself three simp
 le questions: do I use it?\, do I love it?\, will I miss it? If you answere
 d NO to these questions\, pack it up for the yard sale!\n\nWe are collectin
 g books\, household items\, video games\, small appliances\, pictures\, too
 ls\,\nelectronics\, furniture\, toys and anything else you can think of (pl
 ease\, no clothes). You can bring in your items and leave them in the Guild
  Room. Don’t forget to tell your family and friends!\n\nAs you can imagine\
 , many hours go into preparing for this fundraiser\, and we are looking for
 \nvolunteers to help clean\, organize\, price and pack up items for the sal
 e. We will get together:  Thursday Mornings (9:00 am – 12:00 pm) on April 9
 \, 16\, 23 and 30 AND Monday Evenings (7:00 – 9:00 pm) on April 13\, 20 and
  27. Please contact the church office if you're interested in helping out.
LAST-MODIFIED:20150413T175622Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:FCC Yard Sale\, 9am-2pm
TRANSP:OPAQUE
