DESCRIPTION:Montclair Art Walk\, Friday October 21 from 6-9 pm (we will be 
 one of the venues.)  Go to http://montclaircenter.com/montclair-fall-art-wa
 lk/ for more information.  FCC will have "The Box" on display on the front 
 lawn.  The Box is a replica of a Solitary Confinement Cell\, and is chillin
 g\, tangible proof of how human lives are diminished\,  brutalized\, and in
 stitutionalized in our corrupt and broken penal system.   Stop by to get an
  experience of what it feels like to be inside.  It will be at FCC through 
 Monday October 24th.
