DESCRIPTION:<p>Join us for a special online seminar with esteemed biblical 
 scholar\, &nbsp\;Dr. Obery Hendricks\, author of &nbsp\;<u>The Politics of 
 Jesus: Rediscovering the True Nature of Jesus’ Teachings and How They Have 
 Been Corrupted</u>. &nbsp\;Dr. Hendricks is a professor of Biblical Interpr
 etation at New York Theological Seminary.&nbsp\;<em> “To say that Jesus was
  a political revolutionary is to say that the message he proclaimed not onl
 y called for change in individual hearts but also demanded sweeping and com
 prehensive change in the political\, social\, and economic structures in hi
 s setting in life: colonized Israel\,”</em> Hendrickswrites.&nbsp\;This is 
 truly a conversation for our time and we look forward to sharing it with yo
 u. <br></p><p><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87117522335?pwd=K1NLRStvWD
 Z3R21hcHFxNVU0bTlndz09"><strong><span>CLICK HERE TO JOIN IN</span></strong>
 </a>&nbsp\;</p><p>Password:&nbsp\;210857&nbsp\; Meeting ID:&nbsp\;871 1752 
 2335</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200604T220119Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special FCC Online Seminar on the Politics of Jesus on June 17\, 7p
 m
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
