 span><br></span><span>Peace Islands and FCC will provide the turkeys. Pleas
 e go to </span><a href="http://www.tinyurl.com/thanksgivingNov20" id="ow168
 4" __is_owner="true"><span>www.tinyurl.com/thanksgivingNov20</span></a><spa
 n> to RSVP.&nbsp\; You can also signup here to bring a food contribution or
  make a monetary contribution.</span> <br></p><p><span>We're trying to get 
 an idea of how many people (adults and children) are coming so we'll know h
 ow much food to prepare so please RSVP if you'll be there.&nbsp\; Last year
  was a full house with over 100 people attending so be sure to sign up now!
 &nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span></p><p><span>Contact Deb Duhamel at </span><a href="m
 ailto:debbieduhamel@hotmail.com" id="ow1694" __is_owner="true"><span>debbie
 duhamel@hotmail.com</span></a> <span>if you have any questions .</span></p>
 <p>&nbsp\;</p>
