DESCRIPTION:Join us on Fridays Sept 13\, 20 &amp\; 27 from 4:30-6:30pm on t
 he front walk of the church<br>&nbsp\;<br>Peace Café is a way of extending 
 our radical hospitality to the wider community of Montclair.&nbsp\; The ide
 a is simple: offer a cup of coffee and some friendly conversation to folks 
 walking by our church after a long day at work or school. <br><br>We have a
  great crew on board to make this happen\, but would love to have friendly 
 FCC faces around to welcome anyone who stops by.&nbsp\; Please feel free to
  join us any time between 4:30 and 6:30pm and contact Deb Duhamel at <a hre
 f="mailto:debbieduhamel@hotmail.com" id="ow1429" __is_owner="true">debbiedu
 hamel@hotmail.com</a> if you'd like to volunteer.<br><br>We will also be of
 fering our "prayer flag" table for anyone who would like to write a prayer 
 and have it flown on the front lawn of our church.&nbsp\; Prayers can be fo
 r anything: peace\, hope\, grace\, forgiveness ...anything on your heart. <
 br><br>Join us as we bring our community a little bit closer together!
LAST-MODIFIED:20190903T191954Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Peace Café :  It's all about coffee\, conversation and community!  
 Three Fridays Sept 13\, 20 & 27
TRANSP:OPAQUE
