DESCRIPTION:<br><br>We'll be collecting FROZEN turkeys and other canned and
  packaged Thanksgiving goods from 9am-2pm in the back parking lot. There wi
 ll be a truck here from Community Food Bank of New Jersey <a href="https://
 www.cfbnj.org/">https://www.cfbnj.org/</a> .<br><p><span><u><b>Food donatio
 ns and volunteers needed:</b></u>&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Help a local family have a 
 happy Thanksgiving by contributing to our food drive for the&nbsp\; Communi
 ty Food Bank of New Jersey.&nbsp\; CFB provides food for area soup kitchens
 \, shelters and food pantries throughout northern NJ.&nbsp\;</span> <br></p
 ><p><span><u><b>Most needed items:</b></u>&nbsp\; Frozen</span><span> Turke
 ys\, Canned Yams &amp\; Sweet Potatoes\, Gravy (packs and cans)\, Cranberry
  Sauce\, Canned Vegetables\, Stuffing&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Mixes\, Instant Mashed 
 Potatoes\, Applesauce\, Canned Fruits\, Beverages and Boxed Desserts.&nbsp\
 ;</span> <br></p><p><span><b>Donations should be dropped off in the church 
 parking lot</b>.&nbsp\; </span><span>If you cannot stop by on Nov. 23rd ple
 ase feel free to bring in your donations earlier (but no turkeys\,)&nbsp\;&
 nbsp\; clearly marked “Thanksgiving Food Drive” and leave it in the Tower R
 oom.</span> <br></p><p><span>FROZEN TURKEYS CAN </span><span>ONLY </span><s
 pan>BE BROUGHT </span><span>ON NOVEMBER 23rd and collected in the back park
 ing lot!&nbsp\; Thank you.</span> <br></p><p><span><b>To volunteer to help 
 with the collection of food:&nbsp\;</b>&nbsp\; Please signup by going to </
 span><span><a href="http://www.tinyurl.com/y3hkoo3q" id="ow1854" __is_owner
 ="true">www.tinyurl.com/y3hkoo3q</a> </span></p><p>&nbsp\;</p>
