 r neighbors experiencing housing and food insecurity\, <b>at the old Office
  Restaurant building on Bloomfield Avenue in Montclair. <span>Our next meal
  is on July 8 from 5:15 to 6:30pm.</span></b> MESH guests always look forwa
 rd to FCC meals - they appreciate everything from the delicious food to our
  warm smiles and friendly company.</span><span> </span><br><p><span>There a
 re many ways you can volunteer: make and drop off food\; donate beverages\,
  boxes of coffee\, and treats\; help set up\; greet guests\; serve food\;an
 d most of all\, have a great time with the guests.</span><span><br></span><
