DESCRIPTION:At FCC we engage the scriptures with both heart and mind.  This
  ten-week session is perfect for folks that are familiar with Christianity\
 , but would like a fresh set of lenses through which to understand the scri
 ptures more deeply.  We’ll use the video study course designed by renowned 
 theologian and biblical scholar \, Marcus Borg.  Class will meet in the lib
 rary -- or if numbers require\, in the Guild Room. \n\nThe course contains 
 study guide materials\, so please RSVP to Rev. Ann (acralosky@msn.com) if y
 ou would like to join in. Interested folks are invited to read Borg’s book 
 Reading the Bible Again for the First Time to prepare.
