DESCRIPTION:November 19 is Stewardship Sunday - This is our season of givin
 g to FCC!\nOver the past year we have  shared  many transformative moments 
 as a church family and it is our time to celebrate and commit to another ye
 ar of growth. As a congregational church we are the “owners” of this church
  and the sole source of our income.  Information is being sent to help you 
 make your financial gift for 2018. Remember\, all contributions to FCC are 
 tax deductible — and transformative!  We are grateful for your generosity.
