 alled Love.&quot\;  </em></span>Friday February 21\, 8pm &amp\; Saturday Fe
 bruary 22\, 7pm</b></p><p>On Friday and Saturday evenings\, February 21 and
  22\, the FCC Choir will reprise their formerly-annual and much in-demand C
 ABARET in the Guild Room\, with staging\, lights\, and all manner of glitz!
  The theme will be <strong><em>This Thing Called Love.</em></strong></p><p>
 <em>Proceeds to benefit the Programs of  FCC.</em></p><p>Individual admissi
 on is $20 and includes complimentary refreshments. Tickets may be purchased
  <a href="https://www.eventbrite.com/e/this-thing-called-love-a-cabaret-eve
 ning-at-fcc-montclair-tickets-92031792569" target="_blank"><span>online by 
 clicking here</span></a><a href="http://bit.ly/FCCCabaret2020" target="_bla
 nk"> </a>.</p><p>Please contact Liz Donald at <a href="mailto:liz77donald@g
 mail.com" target="_blank"><span>liz77donald@gmail.com</span></a> regarding 
 <strong>s</strong>ponsorship opportunities and/or to place an ad in the pro
 gram.  Donations are also welcome.</p><p> </p><p> </p>
