DESCRIPTION:<p><span>Slow Motion Adult Bible Study is held every Monday at 
 7:30pm on Zoom for approximately an hour.<br></span></p><p><span>Our method
  is to take our time and dig deeply into Scripture\, bringing in cultural\,
  historical\,theological\, and linguistic&nbsp\;backgrounds and resources. 
 We utilize Queries(questions posed for consideration and opening\, not to g
 arner answers) and cross-referencing. (There are&nbsp\;occasional&nbsp\;div
 es down theological or linguistic rabbit holes.) Participants&nbsp\;are enc
 ouraged&nbsp\;to have their favorite translation of the&nbsp\;Bible with th
 em.</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><b>Please contact Rev. Jack Cuffari at
  <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com">jack@cuffari.com</a> to receive the Zoom
  link.</b><br></p>
