DESCRIPTION:<b><span>The class will be led by Rev. Ann Ralosky and Rev. Jac
 k Cuffari (<u>approximately every other Thursday</u> from Sept 28 through F
 eb 1.)  </span></b>  <span><p><span><b><u>Full Class Schedule</u>:  </b>Sep
 t 28\, Oct 12\, Oct 26\, Nov 16\, Nov 30\, Dec 7\, Jan 4\, Jan 18\, Feb 1\,
  Feb 15</span></p></span>"Reading the Bible Again for the First Time" : <i>
 "This welcome book removes many of the barriers that separate thoughtful pe
 ople from the wisdom of the Bible."</i> -Rabbi Harold Kushner <br> <br><spa
 n>Many folks at FCC are inspired by the fresh interpretation of scripture t
 hey hear during worship but wonder why it sounds so different.  If this is 
 you\, please join us for a thought-provoking exploration in to the scriptur
 es through the book\, <b><u><span><a href="https://firstcongmontclair.us6.l
 ist-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=3c5141d050&e=d2d6
 ac503b"><span>Reading the Bible Again for the First Time</span></a></span><
 /u><span>  </span></b><b><span>by Biblical scholar\, Marcus Borg.  </span><
 /b>Borg offers an accessible and deeply insightful understanding of how to 
 read the Bible through the lenses of history and metaphor that lets the scr
 ipture come alive. To order the book\, <a href="https://firstcongmontclair.
 us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=511bf04c1b&e
 =d2d6ac503b"><span>CLICK HERE.</span></a><span>  </span></span><br><span><s
 pan> </span></span><br><b><span>We will cover each chapter over a series of
  10 weeks\, <u>approximately every other Thursday</u> on Zoom at 7:00pm fro
 m </span></b><b><span><b><span>September 28 through February 1. </span></b>
 </span></b><br><b><span><b><span><u>F</u></span></b></span></b><span><b><u>
 ull Class Schedule</u>: </b>Sept 28\, Oct 12\, Oct 26\, Nov 16\, Nov 30\, D
 ec 7\, Jan 4\, Jan 18\, Feb 1\, Feb 15</span><p><span></span></p><p><span><
 /span></p><p><span>Whether this is the first time you've cracked open a bib
 le\, or you've been reading for years\, you are welcome to join us!  Questi
 ons? Email Rev. Ann <a href="mailto:(acralosky@msn.com)"><span>(</span></a>
 <a href="mailto:acralosky@msn.com"><span>acralosky@msn.com</span></a><a hre
 f="mailto:(acralosky@msn.com)"><span>)</span></a>or Rev. Jack (<a href="mai
 lto:jack@cuffari.com"><span>jack@cuffari.com</span></a>)</span></p><p><span
 ><u><b>Click </b></u></span><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87486762412?
 pwd=N0Z2eVlCNzJPbVM3VmdzZW1GYzZHUT09#success"><u><b><span>HERE</span></b></
 u></a><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87486762412?pwd=N0Z2eVlCNzJPbVM3Vm
 dzZW1GYzZHUT09#success"><u><b> </b></u></a><span><u><b>to join!  </b></u><b
 >Meeting ID: 874 8676 2412<br>Passcode: 985645   </b>Phone only? Dial 646 5
 58 8656  <br></span></p><p><span></span></p><p></p><u></u><u></u>
