DESCRIPTION:<br><h4><span>Sign Up for Amazing Homemade Puerto Rican Food at
  Coffee Hour on April 29th!</span></h4><span>Kathy and Rebecca Vazquez-Rhod
 es and the FCC Youth Group will be hosting a special fundraiser after churc
 h in the Guild Room. <b>Please support our service trip to Puerto Rico</b> 
 and try authentic homemade Puerto Rican food! <br><br>We will be serving…<b
 r>&nbsp\;<br><b><span>"Pernil"</span></b><br>(Pork Shoulder) with "Arroz co
 n grandules" (rice and pigeon peas)<br>and "ensalada de papa (potato salad)
