CREATED:20171107T184239Z
DESCRIPTION:Underground Church travels back to our earliest Christian roots
 .  We seek to recapture the excitement and community of Jesus' early follow
 ers through worship that is simple yet profound\, communal yet personal\, c
 omforting yet inspiring.  We live the questions much as Jesus' friends did 
 as they sought ways to transform the world through the simple acts of a sha
 red and loving community.\n\nLast year\, Underground Church started in FCC'
 s basement\, meeting one Saturday night per month.  This year\, the program
  has evolved to include simple\, communal dinners and worship held in the h
 ome of an FCC family member.  We continue to engage through the reading of 
 a sacred text\, create space to share what is on our hearts\, join together
  in song and end our evening with "Spiritual Take-Out\,"  simple worship id
 eas that bring us closer to God and center us in the Spirit.\n \nPlease joi
 n us in love and community 
LAST-MODIFIED:20171107T184239Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Underground Church Saturday\, November 18\, 5PM. (LOCATION TO BE DE
 TERMINED!)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
