DESCRIPTION:PLEASE NOTE:  THE APRIL SERVICE WILL BE HELD ON FRIDAY APRIL 21
  AT 6:30PM IN THE GUILD ROOM:\n\nCan't make it to church Sunday morning? Ch
 eck out "Underground Church!"\n \nLed by John Rogers\, our Associate Minist
 er\, "Underground Church" is inspired by the spirit of the early church. We
  serve one another communion after sharing wisdom in a circle. We also sing
  the words to one of earliest Christian hymns as a community. And\, we feel
  the joy that comes from this simple style of worship. It is a beautiful ex
 perience to travel back to the roots of the early Christ movement!
