DESCRIPTION:<br><b>TIME &amp\; LOCATION TBD</b><br><br>All are welcome!<br>
 <br>During our Saturday evening gatherings\, the Underground Church travels
  back to our earliest Christian roots.&nbsp\; We seek to recapture the exci
 tement and community of Jesus' early followers through worship that is simp
 le yet profound\, communal yet personal\, comforting yet inspiring.&nbsp\; 
 We live the questions much as Jesus' friends did as they sought ways to tra
 nsform the world through the simple acts of a shared and loving community.<
 br><br>Join us in the transformative power of opening hearts to the Holy Sp
 irit and to each other.
