DESCRIPTION:Join us for an informal no-reservation-needed evening of fun\, 
 fellowship and faith.  We'll provide a delicious dinner\, an engaging servi
 ce project\,  a casual worship service\, scrumptious desserts\, and an oppo
 rtunity to hang out with some fabulous FCC friends .  No need to bring a th
 ing — all you need to do is show up\, join in and be prepared to enjoy your
 self!  You can come and go as you like\, participating in whatever way you’
 d like.\n\nOur meal is supported by a "pay it forward" plan: the suggested 
 donation of $5/person with $20/family max will help fund the next Messy Chu
 rch dinner.  We meet from 6-8pm in the Guild Room.\n
