DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><br>    <br><p><span>It’s that time of year a
 gain-the Season of Advent!&nbsp\; Every year\, we delight in the ritual of 
 creating Advent Wreaths to remind us of this sacred time of inner preparati
 on and divine gestation. Advent signifies a time of waiting patiently and f
 aithfully for blessings yet to come.&nbsp\;<br>Join us as we assemble our s
 ymbolic Advent Wreaths.&nbsp\;</span></p><p><span>If you have one from prev
 ious years\, bring it to be refreshed and redressed! If you've never made o
 ne\, decorate a new one.&nbsp\; Or just come and be with us to enjoy the fe
 llowship.</span></p><p><span><br>All materials will be supplied. Suggested 
 love donation $10-$20 to help offset our expenses. It helps to get a head c
 ount so please RSVP to Rev. Karma Cloud at </span><a href="mailto:revkarmac
 loud@sowisdom.com"><span><u>revkarmacloud@sowisdom.com</u></span></a><span>
  as soon as possible.</span></p><u></u></html-blob>
