DESCRIPTION:Shrove Tuesday Pancake Supper\nFebruary 9th at 6pm - First Mont
 clair House\, 56 Walnut St.\n\nJoin us for our annual celebration of fun an
 d carbs before we begin the solemn season of Lent!  Based on the old Englis
 h tradition of eating pancakes before Ash Wednesday we will provide a speci
 al "breakfast for dinner" feast with the folks of First Montclair House\, a
  senior citizens’ residence in Montclair. And as always\, we’ll have  tradi
 tional Shrove Tuesday-style "pancake races" and silly fun —don’t forget you
 r skillets and aprons!\n\nWe'll need folks to help with set up\, clean up\,
  and to contribute dishes. Contact Lisa Marie Bronson at lisamariebb@gmail.
 com for details.
LAST-MODIFIED:20160125T203720Z
LOCATION:First Montclair House\, 56 Walnut Street\, Montclair\, NJ 07042
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Shrove Tuesday Pancake Supper at First Montclair House (56 Walnut S
 t)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
