DESCRIPTION:<span><strong><span>(Enter from either the back door from the p
 arking lot or the ramp on the Plymouth St. side)</span></strong></span><br>
 <span><span> </span></span><br><span><span><span>Underground Church is a un
 ique and dynamic gathering that combines the intimacy of Jesus&#39\; early 
 community with creative and inventive worship experiences.  In the warmth a
 nd safety of community we explore the scriptures\, live out the questions t
 hrough discussion\,  and share innovative rituals that bring us closer to e
 ach other and to our still-speaking God.  Together we create the unity of s
 pirit that helps us find God&#39\;s presence in the messy and beautiful exp
 erience of living today.  </span></span><strong><span></span></strong></spa
 n>
