DESCRIPTION:July 21\, August 18\, September 15\, October 20 (in church libr
 ary or Creation Room\, TBA) <br><strong><span> </span></strong><br><strong>
 <span> </span></strong><br><strong><span>Join us for a summer of friendship
 \, fun and faith!</span></strong><p><span>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ group
  of First Congregational Church\, and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ communi
 ty we would love for you to join us!  We gather on the first Friday each mo
 nth for a social event (pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\, etc) and on th
 e third Friday of each month we gather for Full Spectrum Spirituality\, a s
 upportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, and 
 delve into our faith and scripture through a queer lens. To learn more\, pl
 ease contact Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).
 </span></p>
