DESCRIPTION:Please join us for FCC's Congregational Meeting\, Sunday\, Octo
 ber 15th immediately following Worship!<p>As a congregational church we are
  responsible for charting our own future.<span> </span>And we are called up
 on to cast our vote when important decisions need to be made.<span> <br></s
 pan></p><p>On Sunday\, October 15th\, we will gather in the Sanctuary immed
 iately after worship for a brief but very important meeting.<span>  </span>
 At that time\, we will approve our budget for the upcoming year.<span> </sp
 an>We will provide an explanation of the numbers and answer any questions y
 ou may have.<span>  </span>We will need a quorum to approve the budget and 
 move forward with our new budgetary year\, so we sincerely hope that you wi
 ll make time for this meeting.<span>  </span><b>Only church members may vot
 e\, but we welcome any interested friends of the church to attend.</b> <br>
 </p><br><b><i>Childcare needed/Parent volunteers requested</i></b>
LAST-MODIFIED:20231006T172358Z
