DESCRIPTION:<span>Underground&nbsp\;Church&nbsp\;is a unique and dynamic ga
 thering that combines the intimacy of Jesus' early community with creative 
 and inventive worship experiences.&nbsp\; In the warmth and safety of commu
 nity we explore the scriptures\, live out the questions through discussion\
 ,&nbsp\; and share innovative rituals that bring us closer to each other an
 d to our still-speaking God.&nbsp\; Together we create the unity of spirit 
 that helps us find God's presence in the messy and beautiful experience of 
 living today. </span>
