DESCRIPTION:Explore the key components of the Christian faith in a thought-
  and faith -- provoking series!  Inspired by the most innovative minds in p
 rogressive theology we’ll engage questions about God\, religion\, Jesus\, s
 alvation\, the cross\, the Bible\, and church.  We’ll begin with a brief an
 d compelling video and then let the conversation begin. Of course we don’t 
 promise answers – that’s not what faith is about!  But we do promise to ign
 ite a conversation that will energize and challenge your faith\, and stay w
 ith you long after it’s over.\n
