DESCRIPTION:Sunday Worship Cancelled Due to Extreme Heat Advisory<br>&nbsp\
 ; <br>Friends\, with heat index temperatures at 115 degrees this weekend\, 
 our un-air conditioned Sanctuary poses health concerns for many of us.&nbsp
 \; In order to avoid risk to any of our members we have chosen to close our
  Sanctuary for Sunday worship.&nbsp\; Thankfully\, we have the option to wo
 rship together at our sister church\, Union Congregational in Upper Montcla
 ir.&nbsp\; Rev. John and I will be worshiping there and we encourage you to
  join us.<br><br><br><b>Union Congregational's worship begins at 10am </b>(
 NOTE\, not 10:30!)&nbsp\; Their address is 176 Cooper Avenue\, Upper Montcl
 air. Here is their website if you want to learn more.&nbsp\; <br><br><br>A 
 decision to close the church for any reason is a significant one and we did
  not make this lightly.&nbsp\; We know that many of us look forward to wors
 hiping together each week.&nbsp\; However\, we also must always put the hea
 lth and safety of our members and staff in the forefront.&nbsp\; We are act
 ively seeking solutions to the heat concerns for the remainder of the summe
 r.&nbsp\; Meanwhile\, we look forward to seeing you at Union Cong or next w
 eek at FCC!<br><br>Peace\, Rev. Ann and Rev. John
LAST-MODIFIED:20200503T045201Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Sunday Worship -CANCELLED FOR JULY 21
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
