DESCRIPTION:<p><span><strong><span>Stand with Temple Ner Tamid </span></str
 ong></span></p><p><span>Over the past few weeks\, many of our communities h
 ave been suffering. Hate is pervasive throughout our society. The Jewish co
 mmunity is healing from the attempted arson on Temple Ner Tamid\, the natio
 n was shocked by the murder of Tyre Nichols\, and the BIPOC\, AAPI\, and LG
 BTQ+ communities are also struggling in their own way with local and nation
 al attacks on their identity and wellbeing. What can we collectively do?</s
 pan></p><p><span>Come together in solidarity as we stand against hate in al
 l it's forms.</span></p><p><strong><span>Thursday\, February 2nd at 6:30pm<
 /span></strong></p><p><strong><span>Temple Ner Tamid (963 Broad St. Bloomfi
 eld NJ)</span></strong></p><p><span>Join leaders\, local and national\, as 
 we stand up to this hatred and add our own words of support and love.</span
 ></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230131T182344Z
LOCATION:Temple Ner Tamid\, 936 Broad St\, Bloomfield\, NJ 07003\, USA
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Interfaith Rally Against Hate Thursday\, Feb 2\, 6:30pm at Temple N
 er Tamid in Bloomfield
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
