DESCRIPTION:\n\nMONTCLAIR BOUNCE! - A festival of Optimism and Resilience!\
 n\nMONTCLAIR BOUNCE is a playful\, town-wide exploration of ways to brighte
 n our days and strengthen our spirits.\n\n\nThe entire community is invited
  to walk the sacred labyrinth at First Congregational Church of Montclair a
 s a form of meditation and centering prayer.\n\nOur labyrinth is set right 
 in the center of our beautiful\, neo-gothic sanctuary and is a replica of t
 he one in Chartres Cathedral in France (just a bit smaller). A labyrinth wa
 lk is a way of opening ourselves up to listen to our souls in a deep and tr
 ansformative way. There are no special skills needed -- just walk and let t
 he movement and meditative silence deepen your awareness of God's presence.
LAST-MODIFIED:20190521T210559Z
LOCATION:40 S Fullerton Ave\, Montclair\, NJ 07042\, USA
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:"Montclair Bounce Week" event: All-day Labyrinth Walk
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
