UID:5p0si3v4f29pak7hpn8sp34poj@google.com
CREATED:20180126T201613Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><span lang="en-US">God is Becoming: &nbsp\;Conversations on 
 Process Theology <span></span></span></p><p><span lang="en-US">&nbsp\;Speci
 al Adult study series:&nbsp\; January 31 &amp\; February 7 at 7:30 in the G
 uild Room<span></span></span></p><p><span lang="en-US">Process theology is 
 a relational way of thinking about the dynamism of life and faith.&nbsp\; I
 t is a theology that believes that everything is interrelated\, everything 
 matters\, and everything has an effect on the energy in the universe.&nbsp\
 ; It began with the musings of 20th century physicist Alfred Lord Whitehead
 \, but has captured the imagination of spiritual seekers from many walks of
  life.&nbsp\; It has informed modern Christian theology in various traditio
 ns and&nbsp\;has even found it's way into Rev. Ann's sermons a time or two 
 (or 20!) and when it does there is always a request to learn more!<br></spa
 n><span lang="en-US"><br></span><span lang="en-US">So on January 31 and Feb
  7 we will start a conversation on this theology with a special adult study
  series.&nbsp\; We will just be scratching the surface\, but we hope it wil
 l spark interest in continuing the conversation!<span>&nbsp\;&nbsp\; </span
 ><span></span></span></p><p><span lang="en-US">&nbsp\;If you are interested
  in joining us\, please RSVP to Rev. Ann Ralosky at </span><span lang="en-U
 S">acralosky@msn.com </span><span lang="en-US">.</span><span lang="en-US"><
 span></span></span></p><p><span lang="en-US">&nbsp\;<span></span></span></p
 >
LAST-MODIFIED:20180126T202131Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special Adult Series - God is Becoming:  Conversations on Process T
 heology 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:First Congregational Church Montclair
