 t 28\, Oct 12\, Oct26\, Nov16\, Nov30\, Dec7\, Jan4\, Jan18\, Feb1\, Feb15<
 /span> <br></p></span><br>"Reading the Bible Again for the First Time" : <i
 >"This welcome book removes many of the barriers that separate thoughtful p
 eople from the wisdom of the Bible."</i> -Rabbi Harold Kushner <br> <br><sp
 an>Many folks at FCC are inspired by the fresh interpretation of scripture 
