 u>approximately every other Thursday</u> on Zoom at 7:00pm from </span></b>
 <b><span><b><span>September 28 through February 1. </span></b></span></b><b
 r><b><span><b><span><u>F</u></span></b></span></b><span><b><u>ull Class Sch
 edule</u>: </b>Sept 28\, Oct 12\, Oct26\, Nov16\, Nov30\, Dec7\, Jan4\, Jan
 18\, Feb1\, Feb15</span><p><span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span>Wh
 ether this is the first time you've cracked open a bible\, or you've been r
 eading for years\, you are welcome to join us!  Questions? Email Rev. Ann <
 a href="mailto:(acralosky@msn.com)"><span>(</span></a><a href="mailto:acral
