UID:hva4l6inv2kbij0l46c20bd8pg@google.com
CREATED:20170508T174148Z
DESCRIPTION:Introducing "Future Church 2.0!" - - What Will the Next Five Ye
 ars Hold?\n \nAbout 5 years ago FCC embarked on a visioning process to help
  guide us into our future.  We called this process “Future Church” and thro
 ugh it we created a blueprint for deeper spiritual and congregational growt
 h.   Since that time we have grown and changed and so have our dreams!  So 
 now is the time for us to revisit our future goals and refresh our vision f
 or the next 5 years.\n \nThis process of “Future Church 2.0” will have seve
 ral steps over several months\, but the first is to gather together a core 
 vision team to meet and brainstorm some early ideas for what our future goa
 ls might be.  We are looking to bring together a group of 10-15 members and
  friends of the church who represent our full demographic mix.  We hope to 
 pull together voices from all ages\, genders\, identities\, races\, abiliti
 es and tenure at the church.  We are looking for brand new folks as well as
  our more seasoned members to join this effort. \n \nWe will meet for a one
 -time launch meeting on Sunday\, May 21 in the library after church (12 noo
 n). The meeting will last for 90 minutes.  If you are interested in being a
  part of this core vision team\, we’d love to hear from you and share more 
 about this project.  Please reach out to Rev. Ann\, John Rogers or Liz Dona
 ld for more information. \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170508T174148Z
