DESCRIPTION:A SPECIAL MUSICAL CHRISTMAS GIFT ON DECEMBER 18!\n\nOn Sunday m
 orning\, December 18\, the choir and instrumentalists will offer the congre
 gation a special musical gift — a presentation of Mary’s Magnificat\, her s
 ong of exultant praise and worship of the God who has just blessed her with
  the promise of the Holy Child\, Jesus.  This beloved text will be woven th
 roughout the service\, sung in both the ancient Latin and English\, by a ch
 oral performance of  J.S. Bach’s Magnificat.  This would be a wonderful opp
 ortunity to bring children\, friends and colleagues to FCC!  \n\nThis gift 
 from the FCC choir is made possible through the generous support of the Mon
 sees Music Fund.\n
