DESCRIPTION:<p>Please join us for Underground Church at 5 pm via Zoom! Toge
 ther\, we will talk\, sing\, and create sacred space that transcends the wa
 lls of our homes.  Like Jesus&#39\; early followers\, we will gather togeth
 er to ease our fears and loneliness by creating a community of love and tru
 st.</p><p></p><p><u><b>To take part in Underground Church</b></u></p><p>Ple
 ase get to your computer\, phone\, or tablet (with camera installed) <stron
 g>at 4:55 pm on Saturday</strong> and <a href="https://firstcongmontclair.u
 s6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=68abfa1c98&e=
 d2d6ac503b" target="_blank"><span><u><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></u></span>
 </a>.  Our meeting ID is 893 7523 0641.  Say yes to any downloads—sometimes
  the software is pre-loaded\, sometimes you have to download the software t
 o begin. If you have technical difficulties with videoconferencing or would
  prefer telephone\, dial +1 929 436 2866.<br> <br>Together\, we will create
  a sacred space to share\, and to hold on to\, that will remind us that no 
 matter how much physical distance we maintain\, we are never alone.  Our sp
 ace will be virtual\, but no less sacred.  All are welcome!</p>
