 ck by popular demand!  We will once again be offering the 8 week bible expl
 oration from  biblical scholar\, Marcus Borg.  As a progressive church\, we
  take the bible too seriously to take it literally\, but what does that rea
 lly mean?  How to we understand it’s origins?  How do we interpret the stor
 ies?  What authority does it have in our spiritual lives?  Join us for a  t
 hought provoking conversation that will deepen your faith! Reservations are
  requested so please contact Rev. Ann.
