DESCRIPTION:<br>Join us on Fridays Sept 14\, 21 and 28&nbsp\;from 4:30-6:30
 pm <b>on the front walk of the church.</b><br><br>Peace Café is a way of ex
 tending our radical hospitality to the wider community of&nbsp\; Montclair.
 &nbsp\; The idea is simple: offer a cup of coffee and some friendly convers
 ation to folks walking by our church after a long day at work or school. <b
 r><br>Please feel free to join us any time between&nbsp\;4:30 and 6:30pm. P
 lease contact Deb Duhamel at <a href="mailto:debbieduhamel@hotmail.com">deb
 bieduhamel@hotmail.com</a> if you'd like to volunteer.<br><br>We will also 
 be offering our "prayer flag" table for anyone who would like to write a pr
 ayer and have it flown on the front lawn of our church.&nbsp\; Prayers can 
 be for anything: peace\, hope\, grace\, forgiveness ...anything on your hea
 rt. <br><br>Also this year we will be engaging our community with a voter r
 egistration table and a chance to sign up for the Garden State Equality Wal
 k.&nbsp\; <br><br>So many ways to share the mission of FCC with our neighbo
 rs!
LAST-MODIFIED:20180907T152326Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Peace Cafe: Fridays Sept 14\, 21 and 28 from 4:30-6:30pm 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
