DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><p><span>Slow Motion Adult Bible Study is held every
  Thursday at 7:30pm for approximately an hour on Zoom\, starting again in S
 eptember.<br></span></p><p><span>Our method is to take our time and dig dee
 ply into Scripture\, bringing in cultural\, historical\,theological\, and l
 inguistic&nbsp\;backgrounds and resources. We utilize Queries(questions pos
 ed for consideration and opening\, not to garner answers) and cross-referen
 cing. (There are&nbsp\;occasional&nbsp\;dives down theological or linguisti
 c rabbit holes.) Participants&nbsp\;are encouraged&nbsp\;to have their favo
 rite translation of the&nbsp\;Bible with them.</span></p><p><span></span></
 p><p><b>Please contact Rev. Jack Cuffari at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.co
 m">jack@cuffari.com</a> to receive the Zoom link.</b><br></p></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230607T201114Z
SEQUENCE:3
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Slow-Motion Bible Study is on Hiatus until September (...changed to
  Thursday nights upon return)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
