DESCRIPTION:Are you looking for a way to serve this community\, meet great 
 FCC folks and have some fun?  Then check out the “Ministry Fair” on Sunday\
 , September 23 during Coffee Hour in the Guild Room.\n\nAt FCC we have six 
 ministries which help share our mission inside and outside this church.  Th
 ey are:\nChristian Education\nCongregational Life\nFaith in Action\nHospita
 lity\nProperty and Grounds\nSpirituality and Worship\nStewardship\n\nOur Mi
 nistry Chairs will be available to speak with you about the work their grou
 p does and how you can play a part. 
