UID:1s50cqbgpbu71a2d4t2h35d8s7@google.com
CREATED:20181207T202720Z
DESCRIPTION:During our Saturday evening gatherings\, the Underground Church
  travels back to our earliest Christian roots.&nbsp\; We seek to recapture 
 the excitement and community of Jesus' early followers through worship that
  is simple yet profound\, communal yet personal\, comforting yet inspiring.
 &nbsp\; We live the questions much as Jesus' friends did as they sought way
 s to transform the world through the simple acts of a shared and loving com
 munity.<br><br><b>We will gather at the home of Deb and Julie Matz-Rees at 
 4pm.</b>&nbsp\;<b> Please RSVP to Julie</b> at <a href="mailto:juliemarie.m
 atz@gmail.com" id="ow387" __is_owner="true">juliemarie.matz@gmail.com</a> a
 nd join us in the transformative power of opening hearts to the Holy Spirit
  and to each other. <br>&nbsp\;<br><b><u>Need a ride?</u></b>&nbsp\; "The U
 nderground Church&nbsp\; Express" will meet you in the FCC parking lot and 
 drive you to our meeting place\, and drive you back after our gathering!&nb
 sp\; <b>Just be in the parking lot behind the church at <u>3:30PM</u></b><u
 > </u>and a member of the Underground Church family will be there to greet 
 you.&nbsp\;
LAST-MODIFIED:20181207T202720Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Underground Church\, 4:00pm (RSVP for location.)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
