DESCRIPTION:<p>The Pre-Ordination Commission Invites the Churches\, Ministe
 rs&nbsp\;and Friends of the New Jersey Association to a worship service&nbs
 p\;of Ordination for<span><strong>John (Jack) Cuffari.</strong></span></p><
 p>As a fitting culmination of his decades of ministry&nbsp\;in a wide varie
 ty of settings\,&nbsp\; Jack Cuffari will be honored with the sacred rite o
 f Ordination in the United Church of Christ.&nbsp\; Currently serving&nbsp\
 ;as the&nbsp\;Interim Pastor of the First Congregational United Church of C
 hrist\, Haworth\, Jack is a member of and Spiritual Director in Residence a
 t FCC\, Montclair\, his home church.</p><p>The Ordination Service will begi
 n at 3pm at First Congregational Church and a reception will follow immedia
 tely after. ALL ARE WELCOME!</p>
