UID:pg0sldriodog0nlmt6ng7v9e18@google.com
CREATED:20170213T170514Z
DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a Messy Church Game Night on February 22nd (
 6:00-8:00 p.m. in the Guild Room). \nWe will have dinner\, an informal wors
 hip service\, and lots of fellowship--with games for children and adults of
  all ages!\n\nThere is a suggested donation of $5.00 per person (no more th
 an $20.00 per family) or a contribution of a salad or dessert\, or help wit
 h clean-up. \n\nPlease let us know you will be there (and if you will bring
  a contribution) by going to www.tinyurl.com/messychurchFeb22 . We look for
 ward to seeing you there!\n\n**********************************************
 **********************************************************\n\nWhat Is Messy
  Church?\n\nMessy Church is an informal and unstructured (“messy”) evening 
 each month that brings our community together mid-week for a simple dinner\
 , an opportunity to work together to create a stronger community within and
  outside our church walls\, or simply just be.\n\nWe will provide dinner\, 
 a brief and informal worship experience\, and either an activity or an oppo
 rtunity to serve our community.  You come and go as you like\, participatin
 g in whatever way you see fit.  This is a great way to offer friendship and
  share in God’s love in a fun\, informal way.\n \n So take a break from the
  mid-week stress\, and recharge yourself with us!\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170213T170514Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Messy Church\, 6-8pm in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
