DESCRIPTION:Each Sunday morning from 9:15 to 10:15 we’ll gather in the libr
 ary to explore the current events of our modern world through the lens of s
 cripture.  We’ll explore and challenge diverse interpretations and deepen o
 ur conversation about how the scripture is sacred for us.  Holli Broadfoot 
 will facilitate the discussion each Sunday morning through an online progra
 m called “the Wired Word.”  All are welcome!  If you would like to learn mo
 re please speak with Holli Broadfoot. \nSPECIAL SERIES FROM NOV.2 - NOV.23:
   "OUR HOLIDAY SURVIVAL KITS" On coping with the challenges of holiday conv
 ersations.
