DESCRIPTION:Each SUNDAY from September 11 to October 9 Rev. Ann will preach
  a sermon series called “What We Need Now: Habits of the Heart to Heal a Fr
 actured World”:\nSeptember 11: “Cultivating Chutzpah and Humility”\nSeptemb
 er 18: “A Community of ‘Others’”\nSeptember 25: “One Plus One Equals Three”
 \nOctober 2: “The Power of A Voice”\nOctober 9: “Rocking and Talking”\n\nWe
 dnesday Evening Conversation Series (Sept 14 - Oct 12\, 7:30pm in the libra
 ry)\n\nEach following WEDNESDAY (from Sept 14-Oct 12) AT 7:30 PM we will ga
 ther for conversation to cultivate these important habits in our own hearts
 .  We will use various chapters in Healing the Heart of Democracy to ignite
  our discussion.  The book may be easily found for sale online.
