DESCRIPTION:FCC’s 3RD ANNUAL YARD SALE!  Saturday\, May 7\, from 9:00 a.m. 
 to 2:00 p.m.\n\nWe are collecting new and gently used items for our yard sa
 le (please\, no clothes). Your items can be dropped off in the Guild Room (
 near the fireplace area).  \n\nPlease do not drop off on Saturdays (since t
 here will be no one here to let you in). \n\nTo help us make things easier\
 , please put books in a shopping bag and clean/dust off items before bringi
 ng them in.\n\nWe need volunteers to help with pricing (Monday evenings fro
 m 7:00-9:00 p.m. and Wednesday mornings from 10:00 a.m.-2:00 p.m.).  Also\,
  if you can help the day of the Yard Sale (for a few hours or the entire da
 y)\, please let Deb or Anne know.  You’ll have a great time!   \n\nIf you h
 ave any questions\, please contact Deb Duhamel or Anne Garty at:\n       De
 b Duhamel       857-891-0951       debbieduhamel@hotmail.com\n       Anne G
 arty       973-746-8309       agarty14@comcast.net\n\nAll proceeds go towar
 ds the ministries of First Congregational Church.\n\n
