UID:1i4n0s2d0covk19ndrat2caais@google.com
CREATED:20200420T155643Z
DESCRIPTION:<br>    <br><p>Join Rev. Ann and the Montclair Interfaith Clerg
 y Association for a special Yom Ha Shoah Community Observance. April 20\, 7
 pm</p>                                            <br>    <br><p><strong>&n
 bsp\;Join our wider community as we observe Yom HaShoah (Holocaust Remembra
 nce Day). We will meet by Zoom\, and after a brief service conducted by our
  community’s clergy we will view an important feature length film.</strong>
  <br></p><p><strong>Witness Theater\, 2018\, 74 min</strong><br>Survivors o
 f the Holocaust share their stories in a unique program - "Witness Theater"
  -led by a drama therapist with high-school students in Brooklyn. The hope 
 is that this sharing will sensitize the students and give some closure to t
 he adult survivors after all these years. The film blends past and present\
 , using the Witness Theatre program as a vehicle for telling the survivors'
  remarkable stories.&nbsp\;&nbsp\; &nbsp\; <br></p><p>Please join us for th
 is important evening of remembrance\, Sponsored by MICA\, Montclair Interfa
 ith Clergy Association. <br></p><p><strong>How To Connect</strong><br>This 
 is a Zoom webinar. The process is a little different than our normal meetin
 gs. You must preregister and you will receive a link in the email from Temp
 le Ner Tamid. It's recommended that you do this PRIOR to the event.&nbsp\; 
 Also note\, the custom link you will be sent will not work until a few minu
 tes before the event time. <br></p><p><strong>Pre-Register Here:</strong><b
 r><a href="https://zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_Zlz1CIoDQ2qMmKGIXjZdMQ"><spa
 n>https://zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_Zlz1CIoDQ2qMmKGIXjZdMQ</span></a></p>
 <p>&nbsp\;<strong>Watching the Film</strong><br>At some point during the ev
 ent\, viewers will be directed to watch the film. The film will be availabl
 e online from 7:30pm for 24 hours. If you wish to view it\, you must view i
 t in that time frame.</p><p>Visit:&nbsp\; <a href="https://vimeo.com/403564
 420"><span>https://vimeo.com/403564420</span></a><br><strong>Password:</str
 ong> Menemsha<br>(enter password in box below "This Video is Private")<br><
 strong><u>Please note:</u> </strong>Password will not work until 7:30pm\, A
 pr 20.&nbsp\;</p><em>This Event Sponsored by MICA\, Montclair Interfaith Cl
 ergy Association.</em><p>&nbsp\;</p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200420T155643Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Yom Ha Shoah Observance (via Zoom) with Rev. Ann and the Montclair 
 Interfaith Clergy Association 
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
