DESCRIPTION:Please join us for a very special Thanksgiving Messy Church  wi
 th Peace Islands!\n\nFCC will share a Thanksgiving celebration with our fri
 ends from Peace Islands. We will share prayer\, song\, and food from our re
 spective traditions as we join together in fellowship. Please plan on parti
 cipating!\n\nPeace Islands and FCC will provide the  turkeys.... please go 
 to www.tinyurl.com/NovMessyChurch to RSVP and sign up to bring side dishes 
 and desserts.\n\n\nWHAT IS MESSY CHURCH?\n\nMessy Church is an informal and
  unstructured (“messy”) evening each month that brings our community togeth
 er mid-week for a simple dinner\, an opportunity to work together to create
  a stronger community within and outside our church walls\, or simply just 
 be.\n\nWe will provide dinner\, a brief and informal worship experience\, a
 nd either an activity or an opportunity to serve our community.  You come a
 nd go as you like\, participating in whatever way you see fit.  This is a g
 reat way to offer friendship and share in God’s love in a fun\, informal wa
 y.\n \n So take a break from the mid-week stress\, and recharge yourself wi
 th us!  \n\n(To offset meal costs\, we are requesting a suggested donation 
 of $5 per person\, max of $20 per family.)  \n\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20161108T170937Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:A special Thanksgiving Messy Church with Peace Islands
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
