CREATED:20230713T173205Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><strong><u>Special Camping Weekend July 28-30!</u> </stro
 ng>Full Spectrum is going camping at LGBTQ+ Oneida Campground in New Milfor
 d\, PA for Women’s Weekend.  Join for a day or rent a cabin for the weekend
 ! Come and enjoy a few days of good drinks and better company. </span><br><
 span> If you’re interested contact Ivy: (347-683-7829). <br></span><p><stro
 ng><span><u>Join us for a summer of friendship\, fun and faith!</u></span><
 /strong></p><p><span>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First Congregatio
 nal Church\, and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for 
 you to join us!  We gather on the first Friday each month for a social even
 t (pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\, etc) and on the third Friday of eac
 h month we gather for Full Spectrum Spirituality\, a supportive group to ta
 lk about our spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, and delve into our faith 
 and scripture through a queer lens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Bog
 gess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230713T173205Z
