CREATED:20160411T153253Z
DESCRIPTION:Road Trip to Freedom: Author Talk with Robin Divine\, Sunday\, 
 April 17\, 2-4pm in the Guild Room.\n\nAll of us have felt stuck in a situa
 tion that feels hope-less. Road Trip to Freedom is one woman's journey of b
 ecoming unstuck by embracing her circumstances and discovering the true sou
 rce of Happiness within. \n\nJoin local author\, Robin Divine\, as she shar
 es the self discoveries that helped her transform from homeless and hopeles
 s to Happy and Whole. If you are strug-gling with being stuck\, then this j
 ourney will remind you that it's often the worst experiences that bring abo
 ut the greatest opportunities for change. You have nothing to lose and only
  yourself to gain.\n\n10% of Book Sales will be donated to FCC. This event 
 is co-sponsored by FCC\, Montclair Center for Spiritual Practice (MCSP) & S
 oWis-dom. Contact Robin Divine to pre-order books at robin@robindivine.com 
 OR\, for event info contact Rev. Karma Cloud at sowisdomcfs@gmail.com.
LAST-MODIFIED:20160411T153303Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Author Talk & book signing with local author\, Robin Divine\, 2-4pm
  in Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
