DESCRIPTION:<span>Experience the shared community of Underground church wit
 h <b>a special Advent worship in the Sanctuary.</b></span><br><span> </span
 ><br><span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic gathering that combin
 es the intimacy of Jesus' early community with creative and inventive worsh
 ip experiences.  In the warmth and safety of community we explore the scrip
 tures\, live out the questions through discussion\,  and share innovative r
 ituals that bring us closer to each other and to our still-speaking God.  T
 ogether we create the unity of spirit that helps us find God's presence in 
 the messy and beautiful experience of living today.  All are welcome</span>
