DESCRIPTION:Messy Church\n\nWednesday January 27! \nPlease join us from 6-8
  pm in the Guild Room. \nNo RSVP necessary! \n\nMessy Church is an informal
  and unstructured (“messy”) evening each month that brings our community to
 gether mid-week for a simple dinner\, an opportunity to work to-gether to c
 reate a stronger community within and outside our church walls\, or simply 
 just be. \n\nWe will provide dinner\, a brief and informal worship ex-perie
 nce\, and an all-ages opportunity to serve our commu-nity. You come and go 
 as you like\, participating in what-ever way you see fit – but knowing that
  we’ll be there on each 4th Wednesday to offer friendship and share in God’
 s love in a fun\, informal way. \n\nSo take a break from the mid-week stres
 s\, and recharge yourself with us! \n\n(To offset meal costs\, we are reque
 sting a suggested donation of $5 per person \nmax of $20 per family.) 
LAST-MODIFIED:20160111T172659Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Messy Church\, 6-8 pm in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
