DESCRIPTION:<span><strong>Reproductive Rights: Keep the Faith and Lift Your
  Voice&nbsp\;</strong></span><br><span><strong>&nbsp\;</strong></span><br><
 span>Join us for coffee/tea and dessert as we discuss the abortion access l
 andscape and how we can take action<strong>. <br></strong></span><br><span>
 <strong></strong></span><p><span>For decades\, the issue of abortion rights
  has&nbsp\;been defined by conservative and right-wing religious voices.&nb
 sp\;In the wake of the Supreme Court decision to overturn Roe V. Wade\, Pla
 nned Parenthood of NJ is teaming with congregations in the Montclair area t
 o host an important conversation on how progressive faith communities can r
 espond to this dramatic reversal of reproductive rights.</span></p><p><span
 >You can register by </span><a href="https://www.weareplannedparenthood.org
 /a/caffeinated-convo-series-post-roe-july"><u><span>clicking here!</span></
 u></a><br><span><em>&nbsp\;</em></span><b><span><em>*The event will be&nbsp
 \;in-person in Bloomfield\, NJ ...with the location to be shared with those
  who register.&nbsp\;&nbsp\;</em></span></b></p><span><strong>&nbsp\;</stro
 ng></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20220630T165501Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:A Post-Roe Caffinated Conversation\, July 6 at 7pm in Bloomfield - 
 *Please Register
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
