DESCRIPTION:Shrove Tuesday Pancake Supper\, February 28 at 6pm \nat First M
 ontclair House\, 56 Walnut St.\n\nJoin us for our annual celebration of fun
  and carbs before we begin the solemn season of Lent!  \n\nBased on the old
  English tradition of eating pancakes before Ash Wednesday we will provide 
 a special "breakfast for dinner" feast with the folks of First Montclair Ho
 use\, a senior citizens’ residence in Montclair. And as always\, we’ll have
   traditional Shrove Tuesday-style "pancake races" and silly fun —don’t for
 get your skillets and aprons! \nThis is an especially family friendly event
 \, so bring the kids!\n\nWe'll need folks to help with set up\, clean up\, 
 and to contribute dishes. \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170213T183039Z
LOCATION:First Montclair House\, 56 Walnut Street\, Montclair\, NJ\,
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
