DESCRIPTION:<span><span><i><b>(FCC Members &amp\; Friends Only - limited to
  25 people. Signup deadline is July 6)</b> </i></span></span><br><p><span>T
 he FCC Green Team invites you on a nature immersion adventure! We will gath
 er at FCC at 8:45 am and drive the 1.5 hours to the Delaware river (or you 
 can meet us there.) We’ll be paddling down a calm river combined with occas
 ional class 1-2 rapids (barely big waves)\, perfect for beginners.</span></
 p><p><span>This trip is family-friendly fun and available for all ages (you
 ngest children must be at least 4 years old and 40 lbs). <b>For more detail
 s on the trip please </b></span><a href="https://kittatinny.com/river-trips
 /rafting/"><span><b>CLICK HERE.</b></span></a><span><u><b> </b></u></span><
 /p><p><span><u><b>Signup/Carpool</b></u><br>We'd like to organize carpools 
 for this event. <b>To sign-up the event and for carpool please </b></span><
 a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdTVmnecXG3SsHMJGVp-O3me_n
 DEJsxS5nU0r2cfer5EYddjw/viewform"><b><span>CLICK HERE.</span></b></a><span>
  Questions? Contact Tracey Stephens at </span><a href="mailto:tracey@tracey
 stephens.com"><span>tracey@traceystephens.com</span></a><span>.</span></p><
 p><i><span>Thanks to the generous funding from the Lilly Foundation sabbati
 cal grant\, FCC is pleased to underwrite the cost of this activity.  </span
 ></i></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230630T194816Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:You're invited to join FCC for a River Rafting Experience on the De
 laware River\, July 15!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
