 h\, but owners as well." The Annual Congregational Meeting will take place 
 immediately after the service on June 5.&nbsp\;<br><br><b>The meeting will 
 be brief.</b>&nbsp\; Two items require a quorum of members so please plan t
 o attend.&nbsp\; &nbsp\;If you are just getting to know our congregation\, 
 you are more than welcome to join us.&nbsp\; It's a wonderful way to learn 
 about our priorities and see our lay leadership in action!<br>We will be ap
 proving the slate of members of the Council for 2022-23 and discussing the 
 2022-23 budget.</span></html-blob>
