DESCRIPTION:Listening for the soul\, our “inner teacher” is listening for t
 he voice of God.  All women of the church are invited to become a part of t
 his sacred circle.  We will silence the “static” in our lives and focus on 
 silent reflection\, journaling\, and engaging in deep conversation on how w
 e experience the Holy in our lives.  Modeled on Parker Palmer’s “Circle of 
 Trust” retreat\, this group requires a commitment to attend each monthly se
 ssion in this counter-cultural approach to spiritual community.\n
