DESCRIPTION:<br>On May 30th\, Rev. Ann will be leading a conversation on Th
 e Divine Feminine at Brew Theology.&nbsp\; <br><br><br>Brew Theology\, led 
 by FCC member Nate Nakao\, is a venue designed for creating interfaith comm
 unity through healthy\, eclectic and meaningful dialogue in a brewery or pu
 b environment. It meets every other Thursday in different locations around 
 North Jersey.&nbsp\;<b> This event will be held at Taphouse Grille\, 344 Fr
 ench Hill Road\, Wayne\, NJ at 7:30pm.</b><br>Head to <a href="http://meetu
 p.com/jerseybrewtheology" id="ow301" __is_owner="true">meetup.com/jerseybre
 wtheology</a> for more details\, to register\, and to check out their other
  upcoming events.
