DESCRIPTION:A Special Labyrinth Gathering to Share Labyrinth Experiences on
  June 26\n\n\nOur labyrinth is now closed for the season (re-opens Septembe
 r) but we are holding a special Labyrinth Gathering tonight\, from 6-8pm\, 
 for anyone who would like to share their experiences on the labyrinth. \n\n
 We are welcoming anyone who has served as a labyrinth keeper as well as lab
 yrinth \nwalkers. 
