DESCRIPTION:In the wake of the violence in Las Vegas\, we will gather in so
 lidarity\, support and non-violence.\n\nPlease join the Montclair Clergy As
 socation on Friday\, October 6\, 2017 at 5:00 PM at Church Street Plaza (on
  the corner of Bloomfield and S. Fullerton Aves.) for an Interfaith Non-Vio
 lent Vigil in response to the recent shootings in Las Vegas\, NV. \n\nWe wi
 ll have brief reflections from interfaith leaders and we will close with a 
 silent candle lighting ceremony and witness. We will respect holidays and o
 bservances happening at the same time particularly for our Jewish and Musli
 m friends and make space within our witness to observe and honor their prac
 tices. \n
LAST-MODIFIED:20171006T143725Z
LOCATION:Bloomfield Avenue and So.Fullerton Ave.\, Montclair\, NJ
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Vigil for Las Vegas\, 5pm on Church St. Plaza
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
