UID:tsug55g0qhvpijb3jd5nbo6ng4@google.com
CREATED:20151207T180057Z
DESCRIPTION:Get in the Christmas Spirit with Messy Church. Please join us f
 rom 6-8 pm in the Guild Room.  No RSVP necessary!  \n  \nMessy Church is an
  informal and unstructured (“messy”) evening each month that brings our com
 munity together mid-week for a simple dinner\, an opportunity to work toget
 her to create a stronger community within and outside our church walls\, or
  simply just be. \n\nWe will provide dinner\, a brief and informal worship 
 experience\, and an all-ages opportunity to serve our community.  You come 
 and go as you like\, participating in whatever way you see fit – but knowin
 g that we’ll be there on each 4th Wednesday to offer friendship and share i
 n God’s love in a fun\, informal way. Due to the holiday schedules\, we are
  meeting a week early this month!\n \nHere's the line up:\n6:00 pm: Dinner 
 and fellowship\n6:45 pm: Informal Worship and dessert \n7:00 pm: Community 
 Service opportunity/activity with options for all ages\n \nFOR DECEMBER:\n 
 \nThis month's theme will engage the plight of refugees\, remembering that 
 the baby Jesus was a refugee himself!  We will learn about the current glob
 al refugee situation through the lens of the Christmas story\, have a speci
 al worship drama\, create prayer flags with messages of peace and welcome a
 nd explore how we can support a Syrian refugee family in Patterson.  \n\n S
 o take a break from the mid-week stress\, and recharge yourself with us!  \
 n\n(To offset meal costs\, we are requesting a suggested donation of $5 per
  person max of $20 per family.)  
