DESCRIPTION:Kindred Spirits for Racial Justice: led by our Moderator\, Emil
 y Jones McGowan.\n\nKSRJ is a special initiative of First Congregational Ch
 urch whose mission is to promote dialogue\, learning and deepen relationshi
 ps between our diverse community.  Throughout the year we will be offering 
 various experiences and programs to help us challenge systems of racial inj
 ustice\, oppression and prejudice in society and in the church.\n\nIn addit
 ion to special events\, we will be engaging in regular monthly conversation
 s on race on the following Saturday mornings: February 25\, March 25\, Apri
 l 15\, May 20 and June 24.\n\nFor more information\, please see Rev. Ann or
  John Rogers\, or email Emily Jones McGowan at ejonesmcgowan@gmail.com 
LAST-MODIFIED:20170404T195404Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Kindred Spirits for Racial Justice "Saturday Sessions"
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
