DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><span>Come and practice some Qigong on Saturday\, Ju
 ne 18th. Part of the Taoist tradition\, this exercise system uses very slow
 \, deliberate movement\,keeping your mind actively involved. The style of m
 ovement helps reduce physical and mental tension to help each of us remain 
 grounded and centered.</span><br><span></span><p><span>This session is a re
 fresher of what has been done to date - so come and learn for the first tim
 e\, or come and practice in the group.&nbsp\;</span></p><p><span>Class is l
 ed by Joanne Kornoelje. Joanne has been practicing Tai Chi and Qigong for o
 ver 30 years. She has taught all levels from children to seniors\, and it r
 emains a daily practice in her life.&nbsp\; Come and give it a try!</span><
 /p></html-blob>
