DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Our next book club selection is "Normal People" by S
 ally Rooney.&nbsp\;</strong> Sally Rooney brings her brilliant psychologica
 l acuity and perfectly spare prose to a story that explores the subtleties 
 of class\, the electricity of first love\, and the complex entanglements of
  family and friendship. <br></p><p>FCC Member Mike Magdalenski is facilitat
 ing this group.&nbsp\; We'd like to make it both a literary and social even
 ing\, so we invite pot luck contributions or light refreshments and beverag
 es as well.&nbsp\; We'll gather at&nbsp\;7:00&nbsp\;with some social time a
 nd begin&nbsp\;book&nbsp\;discussion at 7:30pm.&nbsp\; <strong>Please conta
 ct Mike to RSVP&nbsp\;by Sunday\, March 15th</strong> at: <a href="mailto:m
 ichael.magdalenski@gmail.com"><span>michael.magdalenski@gmail.com</span></a
 ></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20200221T202243Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:FCC Book Club Conversation and Refreshments\, 7pm (please RSVP)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
