 nting: an awakening for today's families</span></b></i><span>......"It's ha
 rd enough to train kids to behave\, but good behavior isn't what Jesus call
 s for in the Bible. He wants hearts and souls that are shaped in vibrant fa
 ith and love toward God and others. How can parents cultivate this in their
  children? </span></p><p></p><p><span>In this book Dr. Michelle Anthony sha
 res practical examples and biblical insight on the spiritual role of parent
 ing."&nbsp\;</span></p><p></p><p><span>Please join us </span><span>even if 
