DESCRIPTION:6:00 – 6:40 pm:  Drop in anytime for dinner and fellowship\n6:4
 0 - 7:00 p.m.  Informal Worship followed by dessert\n7:15 – 8:00: A Puja to
  the Universal Light\n\nA puja is a form of worship from India that include
 s prayers\, chants\, and ritual to one's chosen deity. It is meant to help 
 the devotee feel closer to the Divine through simple acts of reverence. At 
 Messy Church\, we will offer a puja to the One Light\, the Truth that is at
  the heart of all faith traditions.  \n\nIf you would like to help with foo
 d or cleanup\,  please contact Kathleen Korgen at \nkorgenk@gmail.com or 86
 2-485-5335.
LAST-MODIFIED:20160504T151604Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Messy Church\, 6-8pm in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
