DESCRIPTION:Equality Walk is Garden State Equality’s largest annual communi
 ty fundraiser. Last year\, there were hundreds of individuals in attendance
  and thousands of dollars was raised. This year\, to under score the fact t
 hat they are a statewide organization with an unwavering commitment to all 
 of NJ\, they will be hosting an Equality Walk Weekend and holding a total o
 f three separate walks\,&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; representing the three geogra
 phical regions of our great state: north\, central\, and south. <br><br><b>
 FCC is the location for the Northern NJ Walk!</b><br><br>Funds raised at Eq
 uality Walk 2019 will support the innovative work GSE is doing in the areas
  of policy\, education\, and health. Every day\, their team is busy advocat
 ing for the LGBT community in our state and offering programs that can serv
 e as models for other states\, agencies\, and organizations. <br><br><b>We 
 have created a team:&nbsp\; “FCC Montclair Pride” and would love for you to
  join!</b>&nbsp\; Just <a href="https://www.gardenstateequality.org/walk" i
 d="ow2204" __is_owner="true">click here</a> to go the Garden State Equality
  Walk webpage to register\, then once you have created your own page\, clic
 k “team” and sign up for <b>"FCC Montclair Pride!"</b>
LAST-MODIFIED:20190909T170305Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Garden State Equality Walk\, 12 noon at FCC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
