DESCRIPTION:Friday\, April 15 at the Riverside Church in Manhattan at 7:30p
 m\n \nJoin us as we celebrate the installation of new national leadership t
 o the United Church of Christ! The Rev. John Dorhauer will begin a  three-c
 ity installation tour in NYC on April 15.  For more information on the even
 t visit: http://events.uccpages.org/installation.html\n\nA group from FCC w
 ill be attending\, taking the NJ Transit train and subway to Riverside Chur
 ch\, grabbing some local dinner in time to attend the 7:30pm event. \n\nHer
 e are the details:\n•Catch the 5:21 train from Bay Street Station (arrive 6
 pm at Penn Station)\n•Take subway up to Riverside Church\, 490 Riverside Dr
 ive\n•Grab a quick dinner in the neighborhood \n•Installation begins at 7:3
 0pm\n•Return home on 9:32 or 10:41 train to Montclair\nWe'd  love to know h
 ow many folks are interested in going\, so please email Dick Thomas at rtho
 mas14@comcast.net
