DESCRIPTION:‘Yes And’ Spirituality\n\nLadies\, it’s that time of year to tr
 eat yourself and enjoy a weekend of spiritual explorations.  We will examin
 e ways to reclaim our personal voice and empower ourselves to say YES in fu
 n and creative ways.  \n\nThe retreat will be led by Lindsey Turner\, Assoc
 iate Minister\, at Union Congregational Church.  We will return to the Tusc
 arora Inn in Mt. Bethel\, PA (about an hour from Montclair).  The cost for 
 the weekend is $250 for double occupancy and $325 for a single room.  And i
 f you can’t get away for the whole weekend\, you can join us for Saturday o
 nly ($75). Please register by Dec 18th.  \n\nThere will be brochures availa
 ble at FCC.  Attach a check (payable to Union Congregational Church) to the
  form and place it in the offertory basket or register with a credit card a
 t www.unioncong.org. Click the Payments icon on the homepage (towards the b
 ottom.)  \n\nIf you have questions\, contact Phyllis Stone (FCC) at 917-715
 -1059 or contact Kate Khachaturian (UCC) at 973-464-8751.  \n\nHope you’ll 
 be able to join us.\n\nPhyllis Stone\n
