DESCRIPTION:<u></u><u></u><p><span>ON HIATUS UNTIL SEPTEMBER: <br></span></
 p><p><span>Slow Motion Adult Bible Study is held every Thursday at 7:30pm f
 or approximately an hour on Zoom.<br></span></p><p><span>Our method is to t
 ake our time and dig deeply into Scripture\, bringing in cultural\, histori
 cal\,theological\, and linguistic backgrounds and resources. We utilize Que
 ries(questions posed for consideration and opening\, not to garner answers)
  and cross-referencing. (There are occasional dives down theological or lin
 guistic rabbit holes.) Participants are encouraged to have their favorite t
 ranslation of the Bible with them.</span></p><p><span></span></p><p><b>Plea
 se contact Rev. Jack Cuffari at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com">jack@cuff
 ari.com</a> to receive the Zoom link.</b><br></p><u></u><u></u>
