DESCRIPTION:<p>Please join us for Underground Church at 5 pm via Zoom! Toge
 ther\, we will talk\, sing\, and create sacred space that transcends the wa
 lls of our homes.&nbsp\; Like Jesus' early followers\, we will gather toget
 her to ease our fears and loneliness by creating a community of love and tr
 ust.</p><p></p><p><u><b>To take part in Underground Church</b></u></p><p>Pl
 ease get to your computer\, phone\, or tablet (with camera installed) <stro
 ng>at 4:55 pm on Saturday</strong> and <a href="https://firstcongmontclair.
 us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&amp\;id=68abfa1
 c98&amp\;e=d2d6ac503b"><span><u><strong>CLICK HERE</strong></u></span></a>.
 &nbsp\; Our meeting ID is&nbsp\;893 7523 0641.&nbsp\; Say yes to any downlo
 ads—sometimes the software is pre-loaded\, sometimes you have to download t
 he software to begin. If you have technical difficulties with videoconferen
 cing or would prefer telephone\, dial +1 929 436 2866.<br>&nbsp\;<br>Togeth
 er\, we will create a sacred space to share\, and to hold on to\, that will
  remind us that no matter how much physical distance we maintain\, we are n
 ever alone.&nbsp\; Our space will be virtual\, but no less sacred.&nbsp\; A
 ll are welcome!</p>
