DESCRIPTION:<h3><span>Join us on the&nbsp\;</span><em><span><a href="https:
 //firstcongmontclair.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1
 a7788&amp\;id=6f388512b0&amp\;e=d2d6ac503b" id="ow548" __is_owner="true"><s
 pan>livestream</span></a><span> on Christmas Eve at 5pm</span></span></em>&
 nbsp\;<span></span></h3><p><strong><span>Christmas is a time for community 
 and forcaring. This year\, with the dramatic surge in the highly contagious
  Omicronvariant of COVID\, we have made the difficult decision to not have 
 in-personworship services and to offer a livestream of the service from our
  beautifulsanctuary instead.&nbsp\;</span></strong><span><br><br>We know th
 is is a disappointment for many of us who were longing to celebratethis spe
 cial holy day together.&nbsp\; Yet we are so grateful that we have hadover 
 9 months of in person services and were able to celebrate all the joys ofAd
 vent in our sanctuary.&nbsp\; As much as we will miss hearing the story and
 singing the carols in our sacred space\, together\, we do this out of great
  lovefor each other\, care for the most vulnerable and responsibility to ou
 r widercommunity.<br><br>Our service will include the full choir\, a brass 
 ensemble and orchestralchimes\, a special message from Rev. Ann and a shari
 ng of the light -- awonderful Christmas experience.&nbsp\;<br>&nbsp\; </spa
 n></p><p><strong><i><u><span>Please tune into our<a href="https://firstcong
 montclair.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&amp\;
 id=02b829bc6a&amp\;e=d2d6ac503b"><span>Facebooklivestream</span></a> at 5pm
  on Friday Evening.&nbsp\; We will also be recordingthat service and will e
 mail it out to the congregation at 8pm to be watchedanytime Christmas Eve.&
 nbsp\;</span></u></i></strong></p><i><b><span></span></b></i>
LAST-MODIFIED:20211223T221128Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:5pm Christmas Eve LIVESTREAM ONLY Service
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
