DESCRIPTION:<span>As a congregational church we are responsible for chartin
 g our own future.  And we are called upon to cast our vote when important d
 ecisions need to be made.</span><p><span>On Tuesday\, June 13th we will con
 vene via Zoom for a brief but very important meeting.  At that time\, we wi
 ll approve a budget strategy for moving forward and vote on our slate of of
 ficers for the upcoming year.  In order to ensure that we have a quorum for
  this very important meeting at this very busy time\, we will meet online t
 o make it as easy as possible for our church family to attend.  Only church
  members may vote\, but we welcome any interested friends of the church to 
 attend virtually. To join the meeting </span><a href="https://us02web.zoom.
 us/j/7390764283#success"><span><u><b>CLICK HERE.</b></u></span></a></p>
