DESCRIPTION:Please join us for some Soul Soup prepared with love by the chi
 ldren and youth during this month's Soul School!  Whet your appetite for an
  Italian inspired menu of Homemade Tomato Soul Soup\, pesto\, pasta\, bread
  and salad.  Go to: www.tinyurl.com/messychurchmarch to RSVP and sign up fo
 r food contributions.\n\nHosted by Karma Cloud and John Rogers\, the evenin
 g promises to be fun-filled and creative. They will share their Tomato Soul
  Soup Secret Recipe with you and unveil the mural of Divine Inspiration mad
 e during January's Soul School!\n\n****************************************
 ****************************************************************\n\nWhat Is
  Messy Church?\n\nMessy Church is an informal and unstructured (“messy”) ev
 ening each month that brings our community together mid-week for a simple d
 inner\, an opportunity to work together to create a stronger community with
 in and outside our church walls\, or simply just be.\n\nWe will provide din
 ner\, a brief and informal worship experience\, and either an activity or a
 n opportunity to serve our community.  You come and go as you like\, partic
 ipating in whatever way you see fit.  This is a great way to offer friendsh
 ip and share in God’s love in a fun\, informal way.  (The suggested donatio
 n is $5/person with $20/family max.)\n \n So take a break from the mid-week
  stress\, and recharge yourself with us!\n
LAST-MODIFIED:20170320T153256Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Messy Church\, 6-8pm in the Guild Room
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
