DESCRIPTION:<span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic gathering that
  combines the intimacy of Jesus&#39\; early community with creative and inv
 entive worship experiences.  In the warmth and safety of community we explo
 re the scriptures\, live out the questions through discussion\,  and share 
 innovative rituals that bring us closer to each other and to our still-spea
 king God.  Together we create the unity of spirit that helps us find God&#3
 9\;s presence in the messy and beautiful experience of living today.</span>
