DESCRIPTION:<p><span>We will bestarting&nbsp\;up Slow Motion Adult Bible St
 udy beginningat 7:30 on Monday\, September 14th. The classes will be approx
 imately an hour\,and will be held via Zoom.</span></p><p><span>Our method i
 s to takeour time and dig deeply into Scripture\, bringing in cultural\, hi
 storical\,theological\, and linguistic&nbsp\;backgrounds and resources. We 
 utilize Queries(questions posed for consideration and opening\, not to garn
 er answers) andcross-referencing. (There are&nbsp\;occasional&nbsp\;dives d
 own theological orlinguistic rabbit holes.) Participants&nbsp\;are encourag
 ed&nbsp\;to have theirfavorite translation of the&nbsp\;Bible with them.</s
 pan> <br></p><p><span>As this is a newchurch / academic year\, the first se
 ssion will be a backgrounding orientationon how the&nbsp\;process goes\, so
 me structural&nbsp\;notes\, and other basics inBible study for Progressive 
 Christians.&nbsp\;</span> <br></p><p><span>Then we will begin ourstudy with
  the Book of Genesis. As we proceed&nbsp\;we will stop and go intocertain n
 arratives in greater depth.</span>&nbsp\;</p><p><b>Please contact Rev. Jack
  Cuffari at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com" id="ow1008" __is_owner="true"
 >jack@cuffari.com</a> to receive the Zoom link.</b><br></p>
