UID:0qm2j5fm5eed7d3pm2jae3vqfj@google.com
CREATED:20230512T174108Z
DESCRIPTION:<u></u><span>Weekly: Wednesdays 11am-1pm in the Sanctuary</span
 ><span> </span><span></span><i> </i><p></p><p><span>Take your soul for a wa
 lk on the labyrinth.  We are pleased to offer labyrinth walks each Wednesda
 y in the mid-day as a chance to connect with your soul in our beautiful san
 ctuary. <br><br>The labyrinth is an ancient spiritual tool \, a mode of “wa
 lking prayer” that invites us to go deeper in our walk with God.  Our labyr
 inth\, modeled on one in Chartes Cathedral in France\, sits as the center o
 f our Sanctuary\, a constant metaphor for our spiritual lives.  Just like t
 he labyrinth\, our lives are not linear\, but filled with twists and turns.
   Sometimes we make great progress\, and other times we feel we are going b
 ackwards.  But if we trust in the path we will find ourselves in the center
  -- the heart of God.</span> <br></p><p><span>All are welcome to take their
  souls out for a healing walk... no experience necessary! </span> <a href="
 https://www.google.com/url?q=https://baristanet.com/2014/03/labyrinth-walk-
 meditation-satisfies-soul/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;u
 sg=AOvVaw0Y_UBYHduSYmZAtn0VUHmP" target="_blank"><span>Check out this lovel
 y write up on Baristanet</span></a> <span>from the Spring 2014.</span> <br>
 </p><p><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.youtube.com/watch?
 time_continue%3D2%26v%3DD453ajtWb74%26feature%3Demb_logo&amp\;sa=D&amp\;sou
 rce=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw0jnAO_0I_l5nW8Ob7EnbtQ" target="_bla
 nk"><span>Watch this video</span></a> <span>to find out more about walking 
 the labyrinth. If you’ve never done so come out one Wednesday evening and g
 ive it a try. It is a wonderful way to nourish your soul and spend some qui
 et time in prayer or meditation.</span></p><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20230607T195401Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Weekly Labyrinth Walks\, Wednesdays 11am-1pm
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
