DESCRIPTION:Bridges Outreach is a volunteer organization that delivers thou
 sands of lunches every year to NY and NJ neighborhoods in need. FCC has vol
 unteered to provide 250 non-perishable brown bag lunches to the Harmony Hou
 se in Newark on Saturday June 15.<br><br><u>There are multiple ways you can
  help us meet this goal:</u><br>&nbsp\; <br><br><b>1. <u>Donations:</u> </b
 >We need specific food donations and <b>will be accepting donations in the 
 Narthex until Sunday June 9</b>. We need the following items:<br>•&nbsp\;&n
 bsp\;&nbsp\; 6-8 oz water bottles<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Chicken or tuna
  salad packets with crackers (not a can of tuna or chicken)<br>•&nbsp\;&nbs
 p\;&nbsp\; Fruit cups<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Unsweetened applesauce<br>•
 &nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Plastic spoons<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Cereal bars\
 , nutri-grain bars\, or granola bars<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Small bags o
 f nuts\, trail mix\, goldfish\, or pretzels<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Brown
  paper lunch bags<br><br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\;&nbsp\; Monetary donations are also
  acceptable<br><b>2. <u>Volunteers:</u> We need volunteers to pack lunches 
 on June 9 during coffee hour\, and to deliver lunches from 9:00 AM – 1:00 P
 M on Saturday June 15.</b> We are limited to 15 volunteers per run\, so ple
 ase respond quickly before spots get filled up.<br><br><b>Please contact Fa
 ith in Action chair Jose Ortiz</b> at 201-314-1342 or at <a href="mailto:Jo
 semortiz1981@gmail.com" id="ow556" __is_owner="true">Josemortiz1981@gmail.c
 om</a> to volunteer or learn more about how you can help.
LAST-MODIFIED:20190614T215947Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Volunteers Delivering Bagged Lunches to communities in need in Newa
 rk - 9am-1pm
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
