DESCRIPTION:Visit to Peace Islands Institute April 20\, 7:00pm\n\nAfter sha
 ring a very special and meaningful worship and visit with us on March 6\, o
 ur Muslim friends from the Peace Islands Institute are eager to have us joi
 n them in their headquarters in Hasbrouck Heights\, NJ. \n\nWe’ll share foo
 d and fellowship and learn more about their mission to foster interfaith di
 alogue and understanding.  Our friends from Union Congregational Church wil
 l be joining us as well.\n\nFor those who want to carpool\, we’ll leave the
  FCC parking lot at 6:15pm. Please RSVP to Rev. Ann and let her know if you
  are willing to drive.  You can check out the website www.peaceislands.org 
 to find out more about this organization.
