DESCRIPTION:<span><b><u>Please note:</u> Today (May 18) will be the last Un
 derground Church until September.</b></span><span><b> </b> <br></span><br><
 span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic gathering that combines the
  intimacy of Jesus' early community with creative and inventive worship exp
 eriences.  In the warmth and safety of community we explore the scriptures\
 , live out the questions through discussion\,  and share innovative rituals
  that bring us closer to each other and to our still-speaking God. Together
  we create the unity of spirit that helps us find God's presence in the mes
 sy and beautiful experience of living today.  All are welcome.</span>
