DTSTAMP:20260401T043557Z
UID:7s2k73q610df96n3hat407be5l@google.com
CREATED:20240529T202113Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><i><span><b>STAY TUNED FOR NEW DATE SOON! <br></b></span></i
 ></p><p><span>When your body is having challenges\, you can instead use bre
 ath and mind to do Qigong exercises\, achieving the same benefits the physi
 cal practice provides: reducing tension and staying grounded. The I</span><
 span>nner </span><span>Smile Meditation is an example of this kind of Qigon
 g. It takes the power of a smile and directs it inward around the internal 
 systems\, clearing and revitalizing the internal landscape. </span></p><p><
 span>Come and experience this grounding and simultaneously uplifting medita
 tion - we think you will love it!<br></span></p><p><span><i>Class is led by
  FCC member\, Joanne Kornoelje\, who has been practicing Tai Chi and Qigong
  for over 30 years. She has taught all levels from children to seniors\, an
 d it remains a daily practice in her life.  Come and give it a try!</i></sp
 an></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240612T160341Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CANCELED! Qigong and the Inner Smile Meditation at FCC\, June 15\, 
 12Noon at FCC
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
