DESCRIPTION:<span><b>Due to unexpectedcircumstances our Bible Study will be
  cancelled for tonight.</b> We look forward to seeing you next week Thursda
 y.</span><br><span> </span><br><span>We take our time\, looking into histor
 ical context\, language\, and any other disciplines that provide insight in
 to our sacred texts. We will be starting with the Foundations of the Bible\
 , a primer that provides an overview of the structure and background of our
  Jewish and Christian scriptures. That will be the first one or two weeks\,
 and then we will begin looking at specific books. Participants are encourag
 ed to bring their favorite translation of the Bible<b>. </b></span><b> </b>
 <br><b> </b><br><b>Here is the link we will use <u>each week </u>for the cl
 ass: </b><br><span><span><a href="https://us02web.zoom.us/j/87533241357?pwd
 =suSsWRbraJdH9z1MGSF0KeTsF8n36k.1" target="_blank">https://us02web.zoom.us/
 j/87533241357?pwd=suSsWRbraJdH9z1MGSF0KeTsF8n36k.1</a> <br>Meeting ID: 875 
 3324 1357<span> </span><br>Passcode: 481855 </span></span><br><br>If you ha
 ve any questions\, please email Rev. Jack at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.c
 om" target="_blank">jack@cuffari.com</a>.
LAST-MODIFIED:20241101T142444Z
