DESCRIPTION:<span><b>If you've been attending FCC and feel we might be your
  spiritual home\,we'd love to for you to be a part of our New Members' Inqu
 iry Class.</b></span><br><span><span> </span></span><br><span><span>First C
 ongregational Church is an inspiring faith community with a rich history --
