DESCRIPTION:<span>Join us at FCC at 7pm as we celebrate the release of Rev.
  John and Allison Rogers’ album of Shaker music! <a href="https://firstcong
 montclair.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=5a
 bb2d14d2&e=d2d6ac503b" target="_blank"><span>The Shakers</span></a> are a U
 topian Christian community dedicated simplicity\, community\, and radical e
 quality. Founded 250 years ago this summer\, their original music - most of
  which dates back to the 1800s - still speaks to us today! Come hear songs 
 from the album and insights into Shaker life from our special guest Br.Arno
 ld Hadd of the Sabbathday Lake Shakers who will join us via Zoom.</span>
