DESCRIPTION:<p><b><span> </span></b></p><p><span><b>Sadly\, the boardwalk p
 ath is icy with patchy snow so we arecanceling this walk. Thanks so much fo
 r the interest and we will reschedule!</b></span></p><p><b><span> </span></
 b></p><p><b><span>Saturday February 24\, 10am:</span></b><b><span> <b><span
 >Nature Walk in the Great Swamp\, Basking Ridge NJ</span></b></span></b><sp
 an> </span><br></p><p>The FCC Green Team invites you to get outside for an 
 easy accessible nature walk on a boardwalk path in the Great Swamp National
  Wildlife Refuge. Get a close-up view of an exciting array of plants and wi
 ldlife including frogs\, turtles\, mammals\, and birds. Carpool from FCC at
  9am or meet us at the Helen C. Fenske Visitor Center at 10am.</p><p>Access
 ible for wheelchairs\, walkers and strollers. <br>Please note: Park rules d
 o not allow dogs\, even on leashes\, because they disturb the wildlife. </p
 ><p><span>Bring a snack and water. We are not planning for lunch on this ou
 ting.</span> <br></p><p><b>RSVP to</b> <a href="mailto:tracey@traceystephen
 s.com">tracey@traceystephens.com</a>  </p><p>If you missed the Sunday Feb 4
 th showing of the fascinating and inspiring film “Saving The Great Swamp: B
 attle to Defeat the Jetport”\, you can watch it <a href="https://tubitv.com
 /movies/552787/saving-the-great-swamp-battle-to-defeat-the-jetport">online 
 here.</a><br><span><br><b><span> </span></b></span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240223T212519Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:CANCELED! Great Swamp Nature Walk (with FCC Green Team)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
