CREATED:20110321T135654Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b><span></span><span><span>Special Musical Christmas Gift T
 his Sunday!</span></span></b></p><p><span>This Sunday\, the FCC Choir is pr
 esenting a gift to the congregation during the worship service – a performa
 nce of Daniel Pinkham’s Christmas Cantata.  This brief\, exuberant 12-minut
 e work also contains some mystical moments and dancelike segments.  The thr
 ee movements will be woven throughout our worship service.<br><i><b>Accompa
 nying the chorus will be a double brass choir\, 10 brass players!  (And yes
 \, even a tuba…)</b></i><br>Our wonderful 26-member choir has been preparin
 g this piece with great joy (and some hard work!)\, and we are thrilled to 
 offer it to you this Sunday.  Please do come\, and bring a friend if you li
 ke!</span></p><p><span><i>-- Julie Morgan\, David Salyers\, and the FCC Cho
 ir</i><i><b> </b></i></span></p><p><span><i><b>This special  music is made 
 possible by a donation from the Gregg Peters Monsees Foundation</b></i></sp
 an></p><p><span>We will also </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/FCCMo
 ntclair" target="_blank"><span>live stream</span></a><span> worship (you ca
 n view by clicking the link and "liking" our Facebook page.)</span> <br></p
 ><p><span><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanent
 ly closed. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway 
 is next to the playground. </b></span></p><u></u><u></u><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T171638Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special Musical Christmas Service - Daniel Pinkham’s Christmas Cant
 ata!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
