 ectrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First Congregational Church\, and if you are 
 part of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you to join us!<span> O</spa
 n>n the <b>third Friday of each month we gather on Zoom for Full Spectrum S
 pirituality</b>\, a supportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys\,
  ask questions\, and delve into our faith and scripture through a queer len
 s. To learn more\, please contact Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</p>
