DESCRIPTION:<span>Join Cullen McVoy for a follow-up workshop on this insigh
 tful approach to understanding our personalities. This next stage is to unc
 over the many\, often hidden and unexpected ways\, in which your type influ
 ences your daily life and your way of seeing the world. We will begin to un
 lock the magic of the Enneagram\, which can free you to live a more authent
 ic life and discover new depths of your spirituality. If you want to catch 
 up on the Enneagram beforehand\, feel free to email Cullen at <a href="mail
 to:culizabet@msn.com" target="_blank">culizabet@msn.com</a>. Also you can g
 et concise summaries of the types at <a href="https://firstcongmontclair.us
 6.list-manage.com/track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=e5dbb15e3c&e=d
 2d6ac503b" target="_blank"><span>https://www.enneagraminstitute.com/.</span
 ></a></span>
