DESCRIPTION:<p><b><u><span>Welcome Back Sunday Worship\, and Picnic\, Septe
 mber 10!</span></u></b></p><p><b><span>Let's gather together at FCC -- we c
 an't wait to see you again! </span></b></p><p><span><i>And bring your water
  jars for the "Blending of the Waters" ceremony!</i><br> After summer’s adv
 entures we are excited to gather together in our beautiful sanctuary as we 
 begin a new church season!  We'll share inspiring worship\, gorgeous singin
 g by our full FCC Choir and\, of course\, share in our  special “Blending o
 f the Waters” ritual.</span></p><p><span>Come for worship\, stay for a spec
 ial BBQ lunch on the front lawn to celebrate Rev. John's return from Sabbat
 ical!  We’ll provide the entrees and drinks\, we’re asking that you bring y
 our favorite side dish\, salad or dessert.  If cooking is not your passion\
 , we could also use your help with set up and clean up. <i>A sign up will b
 e available soon for the picnic.</i></span></p><p><span>We will also </span
 ><a href="https://www.facebook.com/FCCMontclair"><span>live stream</span></
 a><span> worship (you can view by clicking the link and "liking" our Facebo
 ok page.)</span> <br></p><p><span><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth S
 t. driveway is permanently closed. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive sl
 owly\, our new driveway is next to the playground. </b></span></p><u></u><u
 ></u><u></u>
