DESCRIPTION:<p></p><p></p><p></p><p></p><p><span><span><em><strong>Gather a
 t 6\, program at 6:30\, dinner at 7pm.</strong></em></span></span></p><p>Ex
 perience this special Ramadan tradition through an evening of education\, f
 riendship and food!<span> <br></span></p><p>The holy month of Ramadan is a 
 sacred time for Muslims. Similar to our season of Lent\, it is a time of in
 tentional prayer\,actions and fasting to bring our souls closer to God. One
  of the daily practices is to fast from sun up to sun down each day and the
 n break the fast with an Iftar dinner -- a celebratory time to gather with 
 friends and family ingratitude for God's blessings.</p><p><span>On March 26
 \, our friends from Peace Islands Institute\, have offered to provide a spe
 cial experience to share this tradition with us. They will offer a presenta
 tion on the spiritual and cultural practices of Ramadan and provide a delic
 ious traditional Turkish Iftar dinner for us.  As always\, we will enjoy de
 epening our friendships with this wonderful community!</span><span>  </span
 ></p><b><span>IF YOU'LL BE ATTENDING <u>PLEASE RSVP</u> ON THE LINK BELOW</
 span></b><b><span> <b><u><span>AS SOON AS POSSIBLE</span></u></b><b><span> 
 TO LET US KNOW.</span></b></span></b><span> <span>Peace Islands need to kno
 w how many to cook for.</span><br><br></span><b><span>IF YOU'D LIKE TO BRIN
 G A DESSERT:</span></b><b><span> </span></b><span><span>What we need are <u
 >cookies and brownies</u> (no cakes please.)</span></span><span> <b><span>P
 lease sign up through the link below.</span></b> <span>If you have any ques
 tions please call Deb Duhamel at </span></span><span>857-891-0951.</span><s
 pan>  </span><span><a href="https://firstcongmontclair.us6.list-manage.com/
 track/click?u=62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=10613f0e19&e=d2d6ac503b" target=
 "_blank"><b><span>SIGN UP HERE</span></b></a></span><span><br><br></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250326T192745Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
