 , GreenFaith\, and others to march with the Sierra Club in Montclair’s July
  4<sup>th</sup> Parade!<br><br>The parade route starts in Montclair’s busin
 ess district and ends at Edgemont Park\, going approximately 1.25 miles.<br
 ><br>Consider bringing a homemade sign addressing a Creation Care topic: cl
 imate change\, stop fossil fuels\, recycling\, clean energy\, etc.<br><br><
 b><span>For more info and to signup for this fun opportunity go to: </span>
 </b></span><span><br></span><span><a href="https://act.sierraclub.org/event
 s/details?formcampaignid=701Po00000uPgiIIAS&mapLinkHref=https://maps.google
 .com/maps&daddr=Montclair%20July%204th%20Parade@40.973921\,-74.217754" targ
 et="_blank"><span>Montclair July 4th Parade</span>.</a> </span><span><br><b
 r></span><span>For other questions\,feel free to contact</span><span> <a hr
 ef="mailto:greenteam@ftcmtc.com" target="_blank"><span>greenteam@fccmtc.com
 </span></a>.<br></span><span>Hope to see you there!</span></p>
