DESCRIPTION:Green Team Ministry’s <b>December Meeting </b>will meet <b>VIRT
 UALLY </b>Wednesday\, Dec. 10 at 7pm.<br>(Usually meets 2nd Sundays) 12-1pm
  in the FCC Library<br>Be part of planning events\, celebrating Creation\, 
  and living your faith by taking action for the planet. Email <a href="mail
 to:greenteam@fccmtc.com" target="_blank">greenteam@fccmtc.com</a> <b>for Zo
 om link.</b><br><span> </span><br><span> </span><br><span>Green Team/Creati
 on Justice Ministry monthly meetings: 2nd Sunday of the month\, after worsh
 ip\, in the FCC library. </span><span> </span><span><span><span>Our congreg
 ation is committed to the idea that creation care is central to each aspect
  of our church: our theology and worship\, institutional life and practices
 \, and our partnership and work in the wider community. </span></span></spa
 n><span>Learn about FCC’s climate justice initiatives\, be part of planning
  our events\, and live your faith by taking action for the planet. </span><
 br><span>Check out our Green Team Ministry page here: </span><a href="https
 ://fccmontclair.org/green-team-ministry/" target="_blank">https://fccmontcl
 air.org/green-team-ministry/</a><span> <br></span><span>and read our Creati
 on Justice Covenant here: <a href="https://www.fccmontclair.org/creation-ju
 stice-church/" target="_blank">https://www.fccmontclair.org/creation-justic
 e-church/</a></span>
