 o know more about us?  Then this class is for you! </b></span><p><span>If y
 ou've been attending FCC and feel we might be your spiritual home\, we'd lo
 ve to for you to be a part of our New Members' Inquiry Class. Our first cla
 ss of the session is Sunday\, April 14 in-person after worship.  </span></p
 ><p><span>First Congregational Church is an inspiring faith community with 
