  of this sacred time of inner preparation and divine gestation. Advent sign
 ifies a time of waiting patiently and faithfully for blessings yet to come.
  <br> <br>Join us as we assemble our symbolic Advent Wreaths. If you have o
 ne from previous years\, bring it to be refreshed and redressed! If you've 
 never made one\, decorate a new one.  Or just come and be with us to enjoy 
 the fellowship. <br><br>All materials will be supplied. Suggested love dona
 tion $10-$20 to help offset our expenses.<br><b><span>It helps to get a hea
 dcount so please RSVP Rev. Karma Cloud at </span></b></span><b><span><a hre
 f="mailto:karmicjoy@gmail.com" target="_blank"><span>karmicjoy@gmail.com</s
 pan></a> </span></b><b><span>as soon as possible.</span></b></p>
