DESCRIPTION:<span>Put your faith in action and show up for environmental ju
 stice. The Ironbound section of Newark\, aka the Sacrifice Zone\, has long 
 suffered from unhealthy air\, and still the Passaic Valley Sewerage Commiss
 ion is proposing to add a 4th fossil fuel power plant in Newark. For over 2
  years\, the Ironbound community has opposed this outrageous act of environ
 mental racism. Let’s support clean air and justice in the Ironbound!</span>
 <br><span><br><strong>RSVP to tracey@traceystephens.com\,</strong> 973-202-
 8130 text for carpooling</span>
