 er. You go for a walk around the block and everything seems brighter. Why i
 s this?<span> <br></span></span></p><p><span>"The N</span><span>ature </spa
 n><span>Fix" by Florence Williams delves into what is actually going on in 
 our bodies when we are outside in a natural environment.Exposure to the liv
 ing world<span>  </span>has an astonishing positive impact on our physical\
 , mental and emotional lives.<span> <br></span></span></p><p><span>Join us 
 on June 5 at 7 pm in Room 5 to discuss the surprising findings presented in
  “The Nature Fix”. Come with your questions\, comments and ideas for action
 .<span>  <br></span></span></p><p><i><span>The</span> <span>book</span> <sp
 an>can</span> <span>be</span> <span>ordered</span> <span>through</span> <sp
 an>the</span> <span>Montclair</span> <span>Public</span> <span>Library\,</s
 pan> <span>or</span> <span>purchased</span> <span>at</span> <span>the</span
 > <span>normal</span> <span>spots</span><span>.</span></i></p>
