DESCRIPTION:<span><strong>Interested in becoming an FCC member -- or just w
 ant to know more about us?  Then this class is for you! </strong></span><p>
 <span>If you&#39\;ve been attending FCC and feel we might be your spiritual
  home\, we&#39\;d love to for you to be a part of our New Members&#39\; Inq
 uiry Class. Our first class of the session is Sunday\, April 14 in-person a
 fter worship.  </span></p><p><span>First Congregational Church is an inspir
 ing faith community with a rich history -- and we&#39\;d love for you to be
  a part of our future!  If you have been worshiping with us and are interes
 ted in becoming a member of our congregation\, please join us for 3  classe
 s where we will explore how we believe\, what we stand for and what it mean
 s to become a member. The classes are engaging and fun and a great way to m
 eet other folks at FCC!<br><br><strong>Our first class will be held in-pers
 on </strong><b>immediately following worship on April 14 </b>(location TBD)
 .<strong> Our next two classes will be held on Zoom </strong>on THURSDAY Ap
 ril 18 and THURSDAY April 25<b> <u>at 7:30pm.</u></b> All new members will 
 be welcomed in a <strong>special ritual during worship on May 12.</strong> 
 </span></p><p><span>If you are interested\, please reply to Rev. Ann at </s
 pan><a href="mailto:revann@fccmtc.com" target="_blank"><span>revann@fccmtc.
 com</span></a><span>. It is helpful to know how many folks to prepare for\,
  so please RSVP! </span></p><p><span>To connect to the Zoom Class each Thur
 sday </span><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://us02web.zoom.us/j
 /7390764283%23success&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AO
 vVaw13fjH2v6Yse6iY-GG25Wez" target="_blank"><strong><span>CLICK HERE.</span
 ></strong></a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20240401T205722Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Spring New Members' Inquiry Class begins April 14!  (3 Sessions)
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
