UID:26k3rodq56bttkgqa2atrdm14q@google.com
CREATED:20250509T213316Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><b><span>Join us at our table and represent FCC!</span></b><
 br><span>Our bold\, Open &amp\; Affirming welcome is the hallmark of FCC an
 d we are excited to share it with the community at the </span><a href="http
 s://outmontclair.org/montclair-pride-2/" target="_blank"><span>Annual Montc
 lair Pride Festival.</span></a><span> It's a fun and colorful day filled wi
 th musical performances\, community and a lot of love! </span></p><p><span>
 <b>SIGN UP FOR A TABLE SHIFT:</b> </span><a href="https://docs.google.com/f
 orms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfvnrruLteixwYy-F8f1U7zOdGVUpmZcMSwBnYCeNQjvq7hXg/viewform"
  target="_blank"><u><span><b>CLICK HERE</b></span></u></a></p><p><span>We w
 ill host a table and need a great crew of FCC folks to staff it.  If you ha
 ve a couple of hours to share\, please sign up on our Google form (link abo
 ve). We especially invite our Allies to join us to support this event.  Shi
 fts run from 11:30am to 6:30pm (including breakdown). But even if you can't
  commit to a shift\, we hope you will stop by and celebrate with us!</span>
 </p><p><span><br>Our FCC Pride Fest Coordinator is Neil Fasolino.  If you h
 ave any questions\, please contact Neil at </span><a href="mailto:neilflmt@
 yahoo.com" target="_blank"><span>neilflmt@yahoo.com</span></a><span> or our
  Volunteer Coordinator\, Barbra Murtha at </span><a href="mailto:volunteerc
 oordinator@fccmtc.com" target="_blank"><span>volunteercoordinator@fccmtc.co
 m</span></a><span>.</span></p><p><span>SEE YOU AT PRIDE!</span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250520T205257Z
SEQUENCE:1
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Let's Show Our FCC PRIDE at the Montclair Pride Festival\, June 14!
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
