CREATED:20110321T135654Z
DESCRIPTION:<html-blob><u></u><p><u></u><span>On Sunday\, November 27\, we 
 enter into a new season in the church -- a season known as Advent.&nbsp\;It
 's a time of preparation\, of joyful waiting for the Christ child to arrive
 .&nbsp\; It's a time to open our hearts and make room for God to enter our 
 lives.&nbsp\; Advent has many traditions at FCC and one of our most beloved
  is the "Hanging of the Greens."&nbsp\;</span><u></u><br><u></u><span></spa
 n><u></u></p><u></u><u></u><span><br>Hearkening&nbsp\;back to ancient tradi
 tions\, this service reveals the meanings of many of the symbols of the sea
 sons as we festoon our sanctuary\, our church home\, with evergreens\, ligh
 ts\, and the color purple.&nbsp\;<br><br>With scripture\, song and the ligh
 ting of the Advent wreath we will begin this beautiful season together duri
 ng our Sunday worship. </span><span></span><b><i><span>This is a special se
 rvice you will not want to miss!</span></i></b><p><span><b><span><span>We w
 ill have coffee hour in the Guild Room following worship. </span></span></b
 ></span></p><p><span>We will continue to observe COVID safe protocol by fol
 lowing Essex County's CALI guidelines each week.&nbsp\; <br></span></p><p><
 span>We will also </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/FCCMontclair"><s
 pan>live stream</span></a><span> worship (you can view by clicking the link
  and "liking" our Facebook page.)</span> <br></p><p><span><b><u>FCC Parking
  Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanently closed. Enter from The C
 rescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway is next to the playground. 
 </b></span></p><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u></html-blob>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T171638Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Special "Hanging of the Greens" Worship Service -in the Sanctuary
TRANSP:OPAQUE
