  One-Hour Shifts between 9am-4pm</span></b><p><span>FCC is restoring an ori
 ginal Olmsted Brothers garden design on our grounds. A benefactor has come 
 forward\, a landscaping company is standing ready\, and plants have been or
 dered. The only missing piece is you! We need help putting small plants int
 o the ground. </span><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://www.sign
 upgenius.com/go/10C0B44AAAC28A2FB6-48791122-olmsted%23/&amp\;sa=D&amp\;sour
 ce=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw2lraPNOI4rFivuQqR3f3Un" target="_blan
 k"><span><b>Click Here to sign up</b></span></a><span> for any number of on
 e-hour shifts between 9:00am – 4:00pm.  <i> </i></span></p><p><span><i>Plea
 se bring your gardening gloves and a hand trowel if you have </i>one. </spa
 n></p><p><span>Toni’s Kitchen food truck will be on the premises!</span></p
 ><p><span> </span></p>
