DESCRIPTION:<span></span><span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic g
 athering that combines the intimacy of Jesus&#39\; early community with cre
 ative and inventive worship experiences.  In the warmth and safety of commu
 nity we explore the scriptures\, live out the questions through discussion\
 ,  and share innovative rituals that bring us closer to each other and to o
 ur still-speaking God. Together we create the unity of spirit that helps us
  find God&#39\;s presence in the messy and beautiful experience of living t
 oday.  All are welcome.</span>
