 cial events and spiritual conversations. In lieu of our Friday FSS sessions
 \, <span>we will now be meeting Sundays weekly\, during coffee hour\, in Ro
 om 5 (Parents Room!)</span> We will meet to introduce ourselves\, hang out\
 , and chat about life\, spirituality\, and whatever else comes up! If you a
 re interested in joining this group\, please text Lex at 856-332-7448.</p>
