DESCRIPTION:<h4><span style="font-weight: normal\;"><span>If you've been at
 tending FCC and feel we might be your spiritual home\, we'd love to for you
  to be a part of our New Members' Inquiry Class.</span></span></h4><h4><spa
 n>Our first class was moved to Wednesday\, February 25\, 7:30pm on Zoom.</s
 pan></h4><span>First Congregational Church is an inspiring faith community 
 with a rich history -- and we'd love for you to be a part of our future!  I
 f you have been worshiping with us and are interested in becoming a member 
 of our congregation\, please join us for 3 classes where we will explore ho
 w we believe\, what we stand for and what it means to become a member. The 
 classes are engaging and fun and a great way to meet other folks at FCC!<br
 ><br><b><span>Our <u>SECOND</u> class will be held in-person immediately fo
 llowing worship on Sunday March 1st in the Sanctuary. Then our <u>THIRD</u>
  class will be again held on Zoom Wednesday\, March 4 at 7:30pm.  </span></
 b><br><br><b><u><span>To connect to the Zoom Class each Wednesday </span></
 u></b><a href="https://firstcongmontclair.us6.list-manage.com/track/click?u
 =62bf2ca744bdb8b46fa1a7788&id=3378ed89d3&e=d2d6ac503b" target="_blank"><spa
 n>CLICK HERE</span></a><br><br></span><span> All new members will be welcom
 ed in a</span><b><span> <u>special ritual during worship on</u></span></b><
 b><u><span> <b><span>March 15.</span></b></span></u></b><span><br><br></spa
 n><i><span>If you are interested please email Rev. Ann. It is helpful to kn
 ow how many folks to prepare for\, </span></i><b><i><span>so please RSVP at
  <a href="mailto:revann@fccmtc.com" target="_blank"><span>revann@fccmtc.com
 </span></a>!</span></i></b>
