DESCRIPTION:<b><span>Saturday &amp\; Sunday April 27 &amp\; 28: Sign up for
  One-Hour Shifts between 9am-4pm</span></b><p><span>FCC is restoring an ori
 ginal Olmsted Brothers garden design on our grounds. A benefactor has come 
 forward\, a landscaping company is standing ready\, and plants have been or
 dered. The only missing piece is you! We need help putting small plants int
 o the ground. </span><a href="https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0B44AAAC28
 A2FB6-48791122-olmsted#/"><span><b>Click Here to sign up</b></span></a><spa
 n> for any number of one-hour shifts between 9:00am – 4:00pm.  <i> </i></sp
 an></p><p><span><i>Please bring your gardening gloves and a hand trowel if 
 you have </i>one. </span></p><p><span>Toni’s Kitchen food truck will be on 
 the premises!</span></p><p><span> </span></p>
