DESCRIPTION:<span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic gathering that
  combines the intimacy of Jesus' early community with creative and inventiv
 e worship experiences.  In the warmth and safety of community we explore th
 e scriptures\, live out the questions through discussion\,  and share innov
 ative rituals that bring us closer to each other and to our still-speaking 
 God.  Together we create the unity of spirit that helps us find God's prese
 nce in the messy and beautiful experience of living today.  All are welcome
 .</span>
