 ove our slate of new and returning lay leaders  and discuss the church budg
 et as we look to the opportunities and challenges of the upcoming year. We 
 will need a quorum to make these important decisions so we sincerely hope t
 hat you will make time for this meeting. Only church members may vote but w
 e welcome any interested friends of the church to attend.</span>
