DESCRIPTION:<p><span><strong>Worship Service will be held on the front lawn
  (please arrive at 10:10am for check-in).</strong></span></p><p><span>In ca
 se of rain we will be moving into the sanctuary. We will be social-distance
 d and masks will be required. We will also </span><a href="https://www.face
 book.com/FCCMontclair" id="ow1156" __is_owner="true"><span>live stream</spa
 n></a><span> worship. Please </span><a href="https://fccmontclair.org/mt-co
 ntent/uploads/2021/06/worship-updated-rain-protocol-6-16-21.docx"><span><u>
 click here</u></span></a><span> for details!</span> <br></p><p><span><u><st
 rong>Here's what you need to know:</strong></u></span></p><p><span>•&nbsp\;
 &nbsp\; &nbsp\;Please arrive by 10:10 to give yourself time to check in and
  find your seat<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\; &nbsp\;We will be gathering in 6' circle
 s\, 6' apart. Once you're in your circle please feel free to remove your ma
 sk.<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\; &nbsp\;Please bring you own chair or blanket if poss
 ible - we will provide chairs if needed<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\; &nbsp\;We will N
 OT have coffee hour afterwards<br>•&nbsp\;&nbsp\; &nbsp\;If it may be a lit
 tle chilly on Sunday morning please dress accordingly!</span> <br></p><p><s
 pan><strong><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanentl
 y closed. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway i
 s next to the playground. </strong></span></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T171638Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Outdoor Sunday Worship Service
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
