UID:7vnfgk7q581ro1tebhe6uo5ts9@google.com
CREATED:20250326T205753Z
DESCRIPTION:<span><span>Cullen McVoy is offering a follow-up to his first E
 nneagram workshop where he's inviting you to come and share your thoughts a
 bout which Enneagram type you might be\, and receive feedback from him and 
 the group.<br> <br><strong>If you weren't able to attend the first workshop
 \,</strong> and don’t have any idea of your type\, he will be giving a brie
 f recap of the types. The Enneagram is a powerful tool that helps us discov
 er our personality type so that we're able to understand our motivations\, 
 core beliefs\, and unconscious patterns that drive our behavior. If you wan
 t to explore the types beforehand\, feel free to contact him and he would b
 e happy to bring you up to speed (<a href="mailto:culizabet@msn.com" target
 ="_blank">culizabet@msn.com</a>). Also you can get concise summaries of the
  types at <a href="https://www.enneagraminstitute.com/" target="_blank">htt
 ps://www.enneagraminstitute.com/</a>. You can come to share or just to list
 en. You can be as personal or general as you feel comfortable. All discussi
 ons will be confidential.</span></span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250326T205753Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Enneagram Follow-Up Workshop with Cullen McVoy\, April 12\, 1:00-2:
 30pm
TRANSP:OPAQUE
END:VEVENT
