DESCRIPTION:We are a group of women\, roughly over the age of 65\, maybe re
 tired (whatever that looks like today)\, who meet the<strong> <u>first</u> 
 Friday of each month from 11am to 1pm in the FCC library.</strong> We gathe
 r to form connections and to strengthen our bonds of friendship within the 
 FCC community. It is a time of informal conversation about anything\, and e
 verything\, and nothing. Questions?  See Rev. Heather Cherrey\, or email he
 r at <a href="mailto:revcherrey@optonline.net">revcherrey@optonline.net</a>
 .
