DESCRIPTION:<p>This is our LBGTQ+ community within FCC which gathers for so
 cial events and spiritual conversations. In lieu of our Friday FSS sessions
 \, <span>we will now be meeting Sundays weekly\, during coffee hour\, in Ro
 om 5 (Parents Room!)</span> We will meet to introduce ourselves\, hang out\
 , and chat about life\, spirituality\, and whatever else comes up! Led by L
 ex Lourenco and Jasmin Vrban.<span> </span>If you are interested in joining
  this group\, please text Lex at856-332-7448.</p>
