CREATED:20260327T224053Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><span>Join us on an ecumenical Good Friday journey from Mont
 clair to Delaney Hall\, the ICE Detention Center in Newark. Together we wil
 l pray with our feet\, show solidarity with our immigrant neighbors\, and b
 ear witness to the cruelty towards and crucifixion of immigrants today.</sp
 an> </p><p><span><b>Join us starting at 8am</b> for the full 10 mile walk\,
  or you may join in the first or last section\, or the culminating prayer s
 ervice at 3pm at Delaney Hall.</span></p><p><span><b>8am Gather at First Co
 ngregational Church\, Montclair (40 S. Fullerton)</b><br>• Option: Join us 
 for the first mile from FCC\, Montclair to Christ Episcopal Church in Bloom
 field/Glen Ridge</span> </p><p><span><b>1:30pm Gather at St. Stephen’s Grac
 e Community – ELCA\, Ironbound (7 Wilson Avenue Newark NJ)</b><br>• Option:
  Join us for the 2 mile final leg of the journey from St. Stephen’s to Dela
 ney Hall</span></p><p><span><b>3pm Prayer Service at Delaney Hall\, 451 Dor
 emus Avenue\, Newark</b></span> </p><p><span><b>For RSVP and accessibility 
 info</b> </span><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5kHJhWD
 Rwg50BncOw5lU-GVPRUPQcERj74LLyE5x8Ienlcw/viewform" target="_blank"><span>CL
 ICK HERE</span></a></p>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260327T224110Z
