DESCRIPTION:<span>On the night before he died\, Jesus broke the bread with 
 his friends.  In their last moments together he taught them what it meant t
 o "love one another" as he has loved us.  In this special service we will s
 hare an experience of foot washing and the sacrament of Holy Communion.  Ou
 r service will end as we prepare our sanctuary for the solemn service of Go
 od Friday.</span>
