 :30pm on Tuesday\, August 5th\, with singers Elizabeth Honer\, Genya Muzycz
 ka\, Elizabeth Perryman\, and pianist David Maiullo.<br><br>We will tell st
 ories of spicy romance and scorned lovers to fine dining and hopeful singal
 ongs.<br><br>It will be a grand night of singing stories for all.<br><br><i
 ><b><span>There will be refreshments with the artists following the recital
 .</span></b></i><br><br><i><span>Please note: the Sanctuary is not air-cond
 itioned.  Please dress coolly and comfortably!</span></i><br><br>Suggested 
 recital donation is $20.00.</span><span><br><br></span>
