 s are welcome in the  Guild Room to enjoy stories celebrating the magic of 
 Christmas and Winter  Solstice. Nancy will read from her latest children's 
 book\, Mousekin's Twelve Days  of Christmas. Rev. Karma will share from her
  book\, Once Upon A Winter Solstice.  She might even lead us in a Community
  Sing.<br>  </span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span></span></p><p><span>Bel
 ow are links where you can buy the books or learn more about them and the a
 uthors:</span></p><p><span><span>Mousekin's Twelve Days  of Christmas:</spa
 n></span><br><span>  <a href="https://www.thriftbooks.com/w/mousekins-twelv
 e-days-of-christmas/53943162/#isbn" target="_blank">https://www.thriftbooks
 .com/w/mousekins-twelve-days-of-christmas/53943162/#isbn</a>=<br>  <br>  On
 ce Upon a Winter Solstice:<br>  <a href="https://store.bookbaby.com/book/on
 ce-upon-a-winter-solstice" target="_blank">https://store.bookbaby.com/book/
