 movie nights\, picnics\, etc) <b>and on the third Friday of each month we w
 ill be gathering on Zoom for Full Spectrum Spirituality (instead of in-pers
 on)\, </b>a supportive group to talk about our spiritual journeys\, ask que
 stions\, and delve into our faith and scripture through a queer lens. To le
 arn more\, please contact Lori Boggess (862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (8
 56-332-7448).</span></p>
