 y designed by the Olmsted Firm in1925. Frederick Law Olmsted's vision was f
 or all inhabitantsof cities to meet in green spaces\, breaking down barrier
 sand creating common ground. We're finally able to make that vision a reali
 ty! Join us for a blessing of this beautiful new community space.</span>
