CREATED:20250915T161429Z
DESCRIPTION:<span></span><span>Underground Church is a unique and dynamic g
 athering that meets monthly\, and combines the intimacy of Jesus' early com
 munity with creative and inventive worship experiences.  In the warmth and 
 safety of community we explore the scriptures\, live out the questions thro
 ugh discussion\,  and share innovative rituals that bring us closer to each
  other and to our still-speaking God. Together we create the unity of spiri
 t that helps us find God's presence in the messy and beautiful experience o
 f living today.  All are welcome.</span>
LAST-MODIFIED:20250915T161429Z
SEQUENCE:0
STATUS:CONFIRMED
