DESCRIPTION:<p></p>Blessing of the Animals Sunday Worship Service: <b>All c
 reatures of all kinds are welcome!</b><br> <br>As folks who celebrate the p
 resence of God in all of creation\, we honor the divine spark in our animal
  companions as well.<b>  On October 8\,</b> in honor of St. Francis\, we wi
 ll incorporate a Blessing of the Animals into our Sunday morning service.  
 You are welcome to bring any pet you like -- four legged\, two legged\, no 
 legged! -- to join you in church.  We do ask that your animal be comfortabl
 e in a social setting\, and be kept on a leash as necessary.  You are welco
 me to bring a picture of an animal companion who has passed\, as well.<span
 > <br></span><p><span>Please join us in our beautiful sanctuary for worship
  each Sunday. We will have coffee hour in the Guild Room following worship.
  <br></span></p><p><span>We will also </span><a href="https://www.facebook.
 com/FCCMontclair"><span>live stream</span></a><span> worship (you can view 
 by clicking the link and "liking" our Facebook page.)</span> <br></p><p><sp
 an><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u> The Plymouth St. driveway is permanently clos
 ed. Enter from The Crescent. Please drive slowly\, our new driveway is next
  to the playground. </b></span></p><u></u><u></u><u></u>
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T171638Z
SEQUENCE:2
STATUS:CONFIRMED
SUMMARY:Blessing of the Animals Sunday Worship Service -in the Sanctuary
TRANSP:OPAQUE
