DESCRIPTION:<p><b>Join us for friendship\, fun and faith!</b></p><p>Full Sp
 ectrum is the LGBTQ+ group of First Congregational Church\, and if you are 
 part of the LGBTQ+ community we would love for you to join us!<span>  </spa
 n>We gather on the first Friday each month for a social event (pot lucks\, 
 movie nights\, picnics\, etc) <b>and on the third Friday of each month we g
 ather on Zoom for Full Spectrum Spirituality</b>\, a supportive group to ta
 lk about our spiritual journeys\, ask questions\, and delve into our faith 
 and scripture through a queer lens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Bog
 gess(862-228-1084) or Alexis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</p>
