 57?pwd=suSsWRbraJdH9z1MGSF0KeTsF8n36k.1</a> <br>Meeting ID: 875 3324 1357<s
 pan> </span><br>Passcode: 481855 </span></span><br><br>If you have any ques
 tions\, please email Rev. Jack at <a href="mailto:jack@cuffari.com" target=
 "_blank">jack@cuffari.com</a>.
