DESCRIPTION:<p><span><span><span><b><u>Please note:</u> This will be the la
 st FSS until October. </b></span></span></span><b> <br></b></p><p><b>Join u
 s for friendship\, fun and faith!</b></p><p>Full Spectrum is the LGBTQ+ gro
 up of First Congregational Church\, and if you are part of the LGBTQ+ commu
 nity we would love for you to join us!<span>  </span>We gather on the first
  Friday each month for a social event (pot lucks\, movie nights\, picnics\,
  etc) <b>and on the third Friday of each month we gather on Zoom for Full S
 pectrum Spirituality</b>\, a supportive group to talk about our spiritual j
 ourneys\, ask questions\, and delve into our faith and scripture through a 
 queer lens. To learn more\, please contact Lori Boggess(862-228-1084) or Al
 exis Lourenco (856-332-7448).</p>
