 nspiring faith community with a rich history -- and we&#39\;d love for you 
 to be apart of our future!<span>  </span>If you have been worshiping with u
 s and are interested in becoming a member of our congregation\,please join 
 us for 3 classes where we will explore how we believe\, what we stand for a
 nd what it means to become a member. The classes are engaging and fun and a
  great way to meet other folks at FCC!<span> <br></span></p><p><b>Our first
  class will be held in person</b> on Sunday\, February 16 immediately follo
 wing worship.<span>   </span></p><p><b>Our next two classes will be held on
  Zoom </b>on Wednesday\, February 26\, and Thursday\, March 6\, at 7:30pm.<
 span> <br></span></p><p><b>All new members will be welcomed in a special ri
 tual during worship on March 16.<span> <br></span></b></p><p><b>If you are 
 interested\, please email Rev. Ann at <u><a href="mailto:revann@fccmtc.com"
  target="_blank">revann@fccmtc.com</a></u></b>.It is helpful to know how ma
 ny folks to prepare for\, so please RSVP!<span> <br></span></p><p>To connec
 t to the Zoom Class on Wednesday Feb 26 and Thursday March 6<span>  </span>
 at7:30pm <span><a href="https://www.google.com/url?q=https://us02web.zoom.u
 s/j/7390764283&amp\;sa=D&amp\;source=calendar&amp\;usd=2&amp\;usg=AOvVaw3gh
 BUTWJKAchNyXbzTMAoZ" target="_blank"><span>CLICK HERE</span></a></span></p>
