DESCRIPTION:<u></u><u></u><p><span>&nbsp\;</span></p><u></u><u></u><p><b><s
 pan>A Special Musical Christmas Gift! December 18</span></b></p><br><span><
 span>On Sunday morning\, December 18\, the choir andinstrumentalists will o
 ffer the congregation a special musical gift:&nbsp\; Mary’s<i>Magnificat</i
 >\, her song of praise and worship of the God who has just blessed herwith 
 the promise of the Holy Child\, Jesus.</span></span><span></span><br><span>
 <br><span>This famous and beloved text will be sung in bothancient Latin an
 d modern English translations in a musical setting by composerMark Hayes. T
 his festive arrangement of the Magnificat will include severalinstruments:&
 nbsp\; trumpet\, horn\, oboe\, bassoon\, flute\, violin\, percussion\,piano
 \, and harp!</span></span><br><span><br><span>The music is joyous\, express
 ive\, and celebratory – andwould be a wonderful opportunity to bring childr
 en\, friends and colleagues toFCC!&nbsp\; We hope you will enjoy our musica
 l gift to you!&nbsp\;</span></span><br><span><br><em><span>This special mor
 ning of musicis made possible by a generous gift from the Gregg Peters Mons
 ees Foundation.</span></em></span><span><span><i></i></span></span><u></u><
 u></u><p><i><b><span><span><span>We will have coffee hour in the Guild Room
  following worship.</span></span>&nbsp\;</span></b></i></p><p><span>&nbsp\;
 <br></span></p><p><span>Please join us in our beautiful sanctuary for worsh
 ip each Sunday.&nbsp\; We will continue to observe COVID safe protocol by f
 ollowing Essex County's CALI guidelines each week. </span></p><p><span>We w
 ill also </span><a href="https://www.facebook.com/FCCMontclair"><span>live 
 stream</span></a><span> worship (you can view by clicking the link and "lik
 ing" our Facebook page.)</span> <br></p><p><span><b><u>FCC Parking Lot:</u>
  The Plymouth St. driveway is permanently closed. Enter from The Crescent. 
 Please drive slowly\, our new driveway is next to the playground. </b></spa
 n></p><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u><u></u>
